eary%20Americans%20are%20finally%20getting%20some%20relief%20with%20the%20price%20of%20Thanksgiving%20dinner%20down%204.5%25%20from%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.org%2Fmarket-intel%2Fthanksgiving-dinner-cost-relief-but-still-high-relative-to-recent-years%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Farm%20Bureau%20Federation%2C%20or%20AFBF.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20cost%20of%20a%20Thanksgiving%20meal%20at%20home%20for%2010%20persons%20is%20%2461.17%20this%20year%20as%20compared%20to%20%2464.05%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20prices%20were%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcost-of-thanksgiving-dinner-turkey-food-prices-inflation-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistoric%20high%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20Thanksgiving%20dinners%20at%20home%20are%20still%2025%25%20higher%20compared%20to%202019%20before%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20according%20to%20the%20AFBF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20for%20such%20a%20meal%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.org%2Ffiles%2F2020-Year-to-Year-Prices-AFBF-Thanksgiving-Dinner-Cost_Survey.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2448.91%20in%202019.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AFBF%20based%20its%20assessment%20on%20a%20survey%20from%20all%2050%20states%20and%20Puerto%20Rico%20collected%20between%20November%201%20and%20November%206.%20The%20survey%20includes%20prices%20of%20products%20used%20in%20a%20classic%20Thanksgiving%20meal%2C%20including%20turkey%2C%20fresh%20cranberries%2C%20and%20whipping%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%2016-pound%20frozen%20whole%20turkey%2C%20which%20costs%20%2427.35%20on%20average%2C%20accounted%20for%2045%25%20of%20the%20price%20of%20Thanksgiving%20dinner%20this%20year.%20A%20similar%20turkey%20cost%20%2428.96%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.org%2Ffiles%2FYear_Over_Year_Price_Comparison_22.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elast%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20accounted%20for%20a%20similar%20share%20in%20the%20basket%20of%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fall%20in%20the%20price%20of%20a%20Thanksgiving%20dinner%20comes%20after%20a%20cooling%20in%20US%20inflation%20amid%20relentless%20interest-rate%20hikes%20by%20the%20Federal%20Reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.federalreserve.gov%2Fmonetarypolicy%2Fopenmarket.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eraised%20interest%20rates%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2011%20times%20since%20March%202022%20to%20cool%20soaring%20prices%20that%20rose%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-when-back-to-normal-cpi-federal-reserve-economic-outlook-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E3.2%25%20in%20October%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20year%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20down%20from%20a%20four-decade%20high%20of%209.1%25%20year-over-year%20increase%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-cpi-price-growth-june-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJune%202022.%3C%2Fa%3E%20But%2C%20that's%20still%20above%20the%20Fed's%202%25%20inflation%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20any%20consolation%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20Thanksgiving%20dinners%20is%20likely%20to%20fall%20over%20time%20%E2%80%94%20which%20means%20it%20will%20be%20cheaper%20for%20your%20children%20to%20host%20dinner%2C%20Deutsche%20Bank%20research%20strategist%20Jim%20Reid%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20very%20long%20run%2C%20agricultural%20prices%20have%20tended%20to%20decline%20in%20real%20terms%26quot%3B%20when%20inflation%20is%20taken%20into%20account%2C%20Reid%20wrote%20in%20the%20note%2C%20which%20was%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20price%20of%20wheat%20fell%201.2%25%20per%20year%20over%20the%20last%20150%20years%20while%20an%20index%20of%20food%20prices%20has%20fallen%201.6%25%20per%20year%20since%201947%2C%20even%20after%20accounting%20for%20periods%20when%20prices%20gained%20strongly%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20long-term%20trend%20of%20falling%20food%20prices%20reflects%20improved%20productivity%20for%20commodities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20rest%20assured%20that%20if%20history%20is%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20your%20Thanksgiving%20meal%20will%20probably%20fail%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20general%20inflation%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20lives%2C%20even%20if%20there%20are%20periods%20where%20the%20cost%20does%20increase%20for%20a%20while%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Reid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthanksgiving-dinner-price-cost-before-pandemic-turkey-food-inflation-cpi-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700730245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655ef6089c7d23cb3b9f2808%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthanksgiving-dinner-price-cost-before-pandemic-turkey-food-inflation-cpi-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2010-person%20classic%20Thanksgiving%20dinner%20at%20home%20costs%20an%20average%20of%20%2461.17%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthanksgiving-dinner-price-cost-before-pandemic-turkey-food-inflation-cpi-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Palestinian%20official%20says%20truce%20delayed%20over%20'last%20minute'%20hostage%20list%20details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700729995000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105441378%2Cimgsize-165742.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fp