0a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20stable%2C%20well-informed%2C%20and%20effective%20governance%26quot%3B%20in%20OpenAI.%20Now%2C%20Radhika%20Gupta%2C%20Managing%20Director%20and%20CEO%20of%20Edelweiss%20Mutual%20Fund%20said%20that%20the%20world%20witnessed%20%26quot%3Bwartime%20leadership%26quot%3B%20from%20Mr%20Nadella.%20The%20%26quot%3Bformer%20Microsoft%20intern%26quot%3B%20also%20thanked%20him%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20she%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20in%20the%20last%205%20days%2C%20we%20saw%20wartime%20leadership%20from%20you%20Satya%20that%20no%20management%20class%20can%20teach%20and%20every%20CEO%20can%20learn%20from.%20Thank%20you%2C%20A%20former%20Microsoft%20intern%20%3A)%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAnd%20in%20the%20last%205%20days%2C%20we%20saw%20wartime%20leadership%20from%20you%20Satya%20that%20no%20management%20class%20can%20teach%20and%20every%20CEO%20can%20learn%20from.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThank%20you%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20former%20Microsoft%20intern%20%3A)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FlJcqP5oxxK%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FlJcqP5oxxK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Radhika%20Gupta%20(%40iRadhikaGupta)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FiRadhikaGupta%2Fstatus%2F1727485266758389773%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Ms%20Gupta's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fradhikagupta2%2Fdetails%2Fexperience%2F%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20worked%20as%C2%A0a%20Program%20Manager%20Intern%20%26quot%3Bover%20two%20summers%20(2003%2C%202004)%20for%20Microsoft%20Office%26quot%3B.%20She%20was%20responsible%20for%20conceptualizing%20and%20designing%20new%20features%20in%20Office%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20in%20response%20to%20a%20post%20by%20Mr%20Nadella%20where%20he%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20greatest%20privilege%20of%20my%20job%20is%20working%20with%20people%20who%20are%20driven%20by%20mission.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThese%20last%205%20days%2C%20I%20saw%20people%20across%20OpenAI%20remaining%20calm%20and%20resolute%20in%20driving%20their%20mission%20despite%20all%20that%20was%20happening%20around%20them.%20And%20I%20saw%20people%20across%20Microsoft%20remain%20focused%20on%20our%20mission%20and%20serving%20our%20customers%20and%20partners%2C%20stepping%20up%20to%20help%20in%20every%20way.%20This%20is%20what%20I'm%20especially%20thankful%20for%20going%20into%20the%20Thanksgiving%20holiday.%20Thank%20you%20for%20your%20resolve%20and%20for%20the%20work%20you%20do%20each%20day%20to%20advance%20AI%20safely%20and%20responsibly%20and%20distribute%20its%20benefits%20to%20all%20of%20humanity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20the%20microblogging%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20board%20that%20fired%20Mr%20Altman%20from%20his%20role%20as%20CEO%20of%20the%20ChatGPT%20creator%20has%20been%20almost%20entirely%20replaced%20following%20a%20rebellion%20by%20employees%2C%20cementing%20his%20position%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20firm.%20The%20sole%20survivor%20in%20the%20boardroom%20in%20the%20new%20Altman%20era%20is%20Adam%20D'Angelo%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20question-and-answer%20site%20Quora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20be%20joined%20by%20ex-Salesforce%20co-CEO%20Bret%20Taylor%20and%20by%20former%20US%20Treasury%20Secretary%20and%20president%20of%20Harvard%20University%2C%20Larry%20Summers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700729340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ftb1lcrdg_radhika-gupta_625x300_23_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsaw-wartime-leadership-radhika-gupta-former-microsoft-intern-praises-satya-nadella-4599211%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAnd%20in%20the%20last%205%20days%2C%20we%20saw%20wartime%20leadership%20from%20you%20Satya%20that%20no%20management%20class%20can%20teach%20and%20every%20CEO%20can%20learn%20from%2C%26quot%3B%20Radhika%20Gupta%2C%20Managing%20Director%20and%20CEO%20of%20Edelweiss%20Mutual%20Fund%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsaw-wartime-leadership-radhika-gupta-former-microsoft-intern-praises-satya-nadella-4599211%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsaw-wartime-leadership-radhika-gupta-former-microsoft-intern-praises-satya-nadella-4599211%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsaw-wartime-leadership-radhika-gupta-former-microsoft-intern-praises-satya-nadella-4599211%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20Terrorist%2C%20IED%20Expert%20And%20Trained%20Sniper%2C%20Killed%20In%20Jammu%20And%20Kashmir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Pakistani%20terrorist%20was%20killed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Rajouri%20after%20a%2024-hour-long%20encounter%20between%20security%20forces%20and%20terrorists.%20Four%20Army%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20gun%20battle%20in%20the%20Kalakot%20forests%20of%20Rajouri%2C%20while%20another%20injured%20soldier%20died%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20terrorist%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Qari%2C%20a%20Pakistani%20national%20who%20held%20a%20high%20rank%20within%20the%20Lashkar-e-Taiba.%20He%20was%20sent%20to%20revive%20terrorism%20in%20the%20region.%20He%20is%20an%20expert%20in%20IEDs%2C%20operating%20and%20hiding%20from%20caves%2C%20and%20a%20trained%20sniper%2C%20the%20Defence%20Public%20Relations%20Officer%20(PRO)%20Jammu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20been%20trained%20on%20the%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghan%20front.%20He%20is%20a%20highly%20ranked%20terrorist%20leader%20of%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20active%20in%20Rajouri-Poonch%20along%20with%20his%20group%20for%20the%20past%20year%20and%20is%20also%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20mastermind%20of%20the%20Dangri%20and%20Kandi%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20the%20operation%20was%20launched%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20after%20a%20man%2C%20a%20local%20Gujjar%20at%20Bajimal%20village%20was%20beaten%20by%20terrorists%20for%20denying%20food%20to%20them.%20The%20villagers%20reported%20the%20incident%20to%20security%20forces%20and%20eventually%20a%20massive%20anti-terrorist%20operation%20was%20launched%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20advantage%20of%20terrain%20and%20forests%2C%20terrorists%20resorted%20to%20heavy%20firing%20on%20troops%20killing%20four%20soldiers%20and%20injuring%20two%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20was%20cordoned%20off%20overnight%20with%20the%20induction%20of%20additional%20security%20forces%20to%20ensure%20that%20terrorists%20engaged%20in%20the%20encounter%20did%20not%20escape%20from%20the%20area%2C%20which%20is%20highly%20forested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20army%20commanders%20are%20supervising%20the%20operation%20as%20the%20army%20says%20terrorists%20have%20been%20injured%20and%20surrounded%20by%20troops%20in%20the%20forest%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20two%20terrorists%20were%20believed%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20encounter%20but%20given%20how%20long%20the%20encounter%20has%20gone%20on%20for%2C%20officials%20now%20suspected%20that%20the%20number%20could%20be%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20killed%20soldiers%2C%20three%20are%20special%20forces%20commandos%2C%20which%20again%20highlights%20how%20officers%20always%20lead%20from%20the%20front%20during%20counter-terror%20operations%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20In%20September%2C%20a%20commanding%20officer%2C%20a%20major%20of%20the%20army%2C%20and%20a%20DySP%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20were%20killed%20during%20an%20anti-terrorist%20operation%20in%20Kokernag%20forests%20in%20Anantnag%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajouri-Poonch%20stretch%20of%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20forest%20was%20largely%20free%20of%20terrorism%20since%202003%20but%20terrorism%20reared%20its%20head%20again%20in%202021%20leading%20to%20frequent%20encounters%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20more%20than%2030%20army%20troopers%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20of%20the%20encounters%2C%20terrorists%20have%20managed%20to%20escape%20even%20as%20troops%20remained%20engaged%20in%20protracted%20operations%20for%20weeks%20on%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20forest%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20security%20forces%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20as%20terrorists%20use%20the%20dense%20forests%20to%20conceal%20their%20positions%2C%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20topography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerrorists%20take%20advantage%20of%20treacherous%20mountains%2C%20dense%20jungles%2C%20and%20the%20alpine%20forests%20to%20hide%20their%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700729340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F49sqi85o_rajouri-encounter-pti_625x300_04_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-terrorist-ied-expert-and-trained-sniper-killed-in-jammu-and-kashmir-4598994%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Pakistani%20terrorist%20was%20killed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Rajouri%20after%20a%2024-hour-long%20encounter%20between%20security%20forces%20and%20terrorists.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-terrorist-ied-expert-and-trained-sniper-killed-in-jammu-and-kashmir-4598994%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-terrorist-ied-expert-and-trained-sniper-killed-in-jammu-and-kashmir-4598994%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-terrorist-ied-expert-and-trained-sniper-killed-in-jammu-and-kashmir-4598994%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Explains%3A%20What%20Is%20A%20Deepfake%20And%20How%20You%20Can%20Spot%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20today%20highlighted%20the%20emerging%20t%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-come-up-with-regulation-penalty-likely-for-creating-deepfakes-and-platforms-hosting-them-4598838%5C%22%3Ehreat%20of%20deepfakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20democratic%20processes%20and%20announced%20that%20the%20government%20is%20preparing%20new%20regulations%20to%20address%20this%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIT%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20affirmed%20that%20social%20media%20platforms%20have%20acknowledged%20the%20need%20for%20concrete%20and%20effective%20measures%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20deepfake%20detection%2C%20prevention%2C%20enhanced%20reporting%20mechanisms%2C%20and%20user%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Deepfake%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20deepfake%20is%20a%20type%20of%20synthetic%20media%20that%20uses%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20manipulate%20or%20generate%20visual%20and%20audio%20content%2C%20often%20with%20a%20malicious%20motive%2C%20to%20appear%20authentic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmitsloan.mit.edu%2Fideas-made-to-matter%2Fdeepfakes-explained%5C%22%3EMIT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bdeepfake%26quot%3B%20first%20emerged%20in%20late%202017%20when%20a%20Reddit%20user%20with%20the%20same%20name%20created%20a%20platform%20on%20the%20online%20news%20and%20aggregation%20site%20to%20share%20pornographic%20videos%20generated%20using%20open-source%20face-swapping%20technology.%20Deepfake%20uses%20a%20form%20of%20AI%20called%20deep%20learning%20to%20make%20images%20or%20videos%20of%20fake%20events.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepfakes%2C%20a%20potent%20blend%20of%20real%20and%20fabricated%20media%2C%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20formidable%20threat%20to%20public%20trust%20and%20truth.%20By%20creating%20convincing%20videos%20and%20audio%20recordings%20of%20people%20saying%20or%20doing%20things%20they%20never%20did%2C%20deepfakes%20can%20manipulate%20public%20perception%2C%20spread%20misinformation%2C%20and%20tarnish%20reputations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hands%20of%20cybercriminals%2C%20deepfakes%20become%20dangerous%20weapons%20that%20can%20disrupt%20and%20destroy%20businesses%20and%20governments.%20A%20fabricated%20video%20of%20a%20company's%20top%20executive%20or%20a%20top%20politician%20can%20have%20serious%20repercussions%20on%20a%20company%20or%20a%20country's%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20we%20have%20witnessed%20many%20such%20instances%20of%20deepfake%20videos%20that%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20Most%20recently%2C%20actor%20Rashmika%20Mananna%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20a%20viral%20deepfake%20video%2C%20sparking%20serious%20concerns%20over%20the%20misuse%20of%20the%20technology%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20Indian%20government%20drawing%20plans%20to%20tackle%20the%20menace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenerating%20deepfakes%20often%20involves%20utilizing%20deep%20neural%20networks%20and%20a%20face-swapping%20technique.%20A%20target%20video%20acts%20as%20the%20bedrock%20of%20the%20deepfake%2C%20while%20a%20collection%20of%20video%20clips%20showcasing%20the%20desired%20individual%20is%20amassed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exponential%20growth%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20has%20also%20triggered%20a%20concerning%20rise%20in%20deepfake%20pornography%2C%20where%20hyperrealistic%20images%20and%20videos%20can%20be%20produced%20with%20minimal%20effort%20and%20expenditure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20To%20Spot%20A%20Deepfake%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMIT%20says%20despite%20there%20not%20being%20a%20foolproof%20method%20to%20ensure%20absolute%20protection%20against%20deepfakes%2C%20there%20are%20certain%20indicators%20that%20can%20assist%20in%20determining%20the%20genuineness%20of%20the%20content%20you%20encounter%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20widely%20circulated%20Rashmika%20Mandana%20deepfake%20video%2C%20many%20viewers%20overlooked%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20individual's%20face%20was%20different%20at%20the%20beginning.%20Ms%20Mandanna's%20face%20was%20superimposed%20on%20the%20body%20of%20Zara%20Patel%20-%20a%20British%20model%20and%20influencer%20of%20Indian-origin%20and%20the%20original%20creator%20of%20the%20video.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deepfake%2C%20with%20Ms%20Mandanna's%20face%2C%20manifested%20only%20when%20the%20individual%20fully%20entered%20the%20frame.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20deepfakes%2C%20a%20person's%20lip%20movements%20or%20blinking%20may%20not%20align%20well.%20This%20discrepancy%20arises%20from%20the%20AI%20algorithm's%20potential%20inability%20to%20precisely%20track%20the%20person's%20eye%20and%20mouth%20movements.%20However%2C%20the%20ever-improving%20AI%20makes%20it%20harder%20to%20spot%20what%20is%20fake%20or%20what%20is%20real%20given%20the%20advanced%20technological%20tools%20we%20have%20at%20our%20disposal%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20the%20shared%20responsibility%20for%20deepfake%20content%2C%20IT%20Minister%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20indicated%20that%20both%20creators%20and%20hosting%20platforms%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20potential%20penalties.%20The%20government%20is%20exploring%20measures%20to%20hold%20both%20parties%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20comprehensive%20regulation%20from%20both%20government%20agencies%20and%20technology%20or%20social%20media%20companies%2C%20establishing%20alliances%20to%20develop%20cross-platform%20detection%20tools%20is%20crucial%20to%20curb%20the%20spread%20of%20deepfake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20several%20online%20subscription-based%20tools%20like%20WeVerify%20or%20Sentinel%20that%20can%20help%20detect%20fake%20content.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700729100000%2C%22visu