he%20Chhattisgarh%20high%20court%20in%202018%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20an%20ill%20intention%20to%20harass%E2%80%9D%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20discharged%20my%20duties%20as%20a%20judge%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20high%20court%20till%20October%202018%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20one%20and%20all%2C%20and%20particularly%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20my%20own%20inner%20being%E2%80%A6%20Now%2C%20a%20sudden%20turn%20of%20events%20descended%20upon%20me%20when%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Dipak%20Misra%20showered%20on%20me%20some%20extra%20affection%20for%20reasons%20still%20not%20known%20to%20me%20which%20entailed%20my%20transfer%20to%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20where%20I%20assumed%20office%20on%20October%203%2C%202018.%20My%20transfer%20order%20seemed%20to%20have%20been%20issued%20with%20an%20ill%20intention%20to%20harass%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fchief-justice-pritinker-diwaker-transfer-allahabad-high-court-cji-dipak-misra-collegium-ill-intended%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20judge%20said%20on%20his%20last%20day%20in%20office%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%20explain%20what%20the%20ill%20intention%20or%20alleged%20harassment%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Diwaker%2C%20however%2C%20thanked%20the%20current%20CJI%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20under%20whose%20leadership%20the%20Collegium%20recommended%20him%20for%20the%20position%20of%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorn%20in%201961%2C%20Justice%20Diwakar%20graduated%20in%20law%20from%20Durgawati%20University%20in%20Jabalpur%20and%20enrolled%20as%20an%20advocate%20in%201984.%20He%20was%20designated%20as%20a%20senior%20advocate%20in%20January%202005%20and%20elevated%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20high%20court%20in%202009.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20farewell%20speech%2C%20Justice%20Diwakar%20said%20that%20his%20transfer%20to%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%2C%20although%20unwarranted%2C%20%E2%80%9Cturned%20into%20boon%20for%20me%20because%20I%20received%20immeasurable%20support%20and%20cooperation%20from%20my%20companion%20judges%20as%20well%20as%20from%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Bar.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20been%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20HC%20since%20October%203%2C%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20praised%20the%20Allahabad%20HC%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgreat%20institution%20which%20has%20its%20unique%20style%20of%20working%20and%20traditions%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20matter%20of%20pride%E2%80%9D%20for%20him%20to%20have%20worked%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBalancing%20a%20heavy%20workload%20is%20indeed%20a%20challenge%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court.%20Furthermore%2C%20this%20court%20was%20subjected%20to%20criticism%20from%20various%20corners%20in%20relation%20to%20its%20functioning.%20But%20I%20am%20of%20the%20firm%20belief%20that%20before%20reaching%20a%20particular%20conclusion%2C%20critics%20must%20see%20the%20difficulties%20and%20shortcomings%20prevailing%20in%20the%20institution%20from%20the%20inside%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20retiring%20judge%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20came%20at%20his%20farewell%20function%20in%20Prayagraj%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Justice%20Bibek%20Chaudhuri%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20transferred%20from%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20to%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%2C%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Collegium.%20%E2%80%9CI%20must%20say%20that%20in%201975%20during%20Emergency%2C%2016%20judges%20of%20different%20High%20Courts%20were%20transferred%20by%20an%20executive%20decision%20in%20one%20go.%20After%20almost%2048%20years%2C%2024%20judges%20have%20been%20transferred%20from%20one%20High%20Court%20to%20another%20by%20the%20Collegium%20of%20the%20Honorable%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20one%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Chaudhuri%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcalcutta-high-court-justice-bibek-chaudhuri-emergency-judiciary-executive%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20farewell%20speech%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Chaudhuri%20said%20that%20his%20transfer%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20beginning%20of%20the%20introduction%20and%20implementation%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%201983%20policy%20that%20the%20chief%20justices%20of%20high%20courts%20and%20one-third%20of%20the%20high%20court%20judges%20should%20be%20from%20outside%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20I%20know%20that%20the%20Constitution%20contains%20a%20provision%20under%20Article%20222%20that%20a%20judge%20should%20transfer.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20accept%20the%20transfer%20without%20any%20remorse.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20with%20all%20humility%2C%20I%20must%20say%20that%20judicial%20pronouncements%20are%20there%20that%20Article%20222%20should%20be%20looked%20into%2C%20should%20be%20considered%20very%20sparingly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20received%20utmost%20respect%2C%20love%20and%20affection%20from%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Bar%20and%20therefore%20I%20feel%20sorry%20to%20leave%20you.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20the%20desire%20from%20the%20Collegium%20who%20parted%20me%20away%20from%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Chaudhuri%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700727407000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23134406%2Fallahabad-high-courtfinal.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fallahabad-high-court-transfer-ill-intended-pritinker-diwaker-dipak-misra%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNow%2C%20a%20sudden%20turn%20of%20events%20descended%20upon%20me%20when%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Dipak%20Misra%20showered%20on%20me%20some%20extra%20affection%20for%20reasons%20still%20not%20known%20to%20me%20which%20entailed%20my%20transfer%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20judge%2C%20describing%20the%20events%20leading%20to%20his%20transfer%20in%202018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fallahabad-high-court-transfer-ill-intended-pritinker-diwaker-dipak-misra%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Regulations%20To%20Tackle%20Deepfakes%20Soon%2C%20Punishment%20For%20Creators%2C%20Platforms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20key%20meeting%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20deepfakes%2C%20which%20has%20been%20flagged%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20several%20celebrities%2C%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20that%20the%20government%20will%20bring%20in%20regulation%20at%20the%20earliest%20and%20attempts%20will%20be%20made%20to%20have%20a%20draft%20ready%20within%20a%20few%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20after%20the%20meeting%20with%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20companies%20working%20on%20artificial%20intelligence%20tools%20on%20Thursday%2C%20IT%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20said%20deepfakes%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20new%20threat%20to%20democracy%2C%20and%20accountability%20for%20such%20content%20will%20lie%20both%20with%20creators%20and%20the%20platform%20on%20which%20it%20has%20been%20hosted.%20He%20said%20the%20government%20will%20also%20look%20at%20penalties%20for%20both%20creators%20and%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20four%20key%20issues%20were%20discussed%20at%20the%20meeting%3A%20how%20deepfakes%20can%20be%20detected%3B%20whether%20and%20how%20people%20can%20be%20prevented%20from%20posting%20deepfakes%20and%20whether%20such%20content%20can%20be%20stopped%20from%20going%20viral%3B%20how%20a%20reporting%20mechanism%20can%20be%20implemented%20so%20users%20on%20any%20app%20or%20website%20can%20alert%20the%20platform%20and%20the%20authorities%20about%20a%20deepfake%20so%20that%20action%20can%20be%20taken%3B%20and%20increasing%20awareness%20among%20the%20public%2C%20for%20which%20he%20said%20the%20government%2C%20industry%20and%20the%20media%20will%20need%20to%20work%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaishnaw%20said%20it%20was%20clear%20from%20the%20discussions%20that%20a%20new%20regulation%20is%20needed%20for%20such%20content.%20He%20said%20work%20on%20this%20will%20begin%20immediately%20and%20an%20attempt%20will%20be%20made%20to%20finish%20drafting%20the%20regulation%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20asserted%20that%20accountability%20will%20lie%20both%20with%20the%20creators%20of%20deepfakes%20and%20the%20platforms%20hosting%20them.%20He%20said%20the%20regulations%20could%20be%20introduced%20in%20the%20form%20of%20new%20rules%2C%20a%20new%20law%20or%20an%20amendment%20to%20existing%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlobal%20Content%2C%20Penalties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20digital%20world%20does%20not%20have%20physical%20boundaries%20but%20content%20created%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20will%20have%20to%20abide%20by%20Indian%20laws%20if%20it%20is%20shown%20to%20people%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20penalties%20will%20be%20imposed%20for%20deepfakes%20that%20cause%20harm%2C%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20said%20the%20government%20will%20look%20into%20this%20aspect%20both%20for%20creators%20and%20platforms%20while%20drafting%20the%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20that%20the%20next%20meeting%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20December%20and%20the%20government%20will%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20follow-up%20actions%20taken%20on%20the%20issues%20which%20were%20discussed%20on%20Thursday.%20He%20added%20that%20social%20media%20companies%20and%20platforms%20have%20assured%20the%20government%20that%2C%20until%20then%2C%20they%20will%20take%20all%20possible%20steps%20to%20tackle%20deepfakes%20as%20per%20their%20policies%20and%20guidelines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaishnaw%20emphasised%20that%20free%20speech%20and%20privacy%20are%20issues%20that%20are%20very%20important%20to%20the%20government%20and%20these%20are%20being%20undermined%20by%20the%20use%20of%20deepfakes.%20He%20said%20the%20new%20regulations%20will%20look%20to%20ensure%20that%20AI-generated%20synthetic%20content%20is%20not%20harmful%20to%20society%20and%20democracy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsers%20have%20a%20right%20to%20know%20what%20is%20natural%20and%20what%20is%20not.%20What%20is%20natural%20and%20what%20is%20synthetic.%20The%20way%20we%20will%20structure%20the%20entire%20regulatory%20mechanism%20is%20that%20we%20will%20focus%20both%20on%20preventing%20harm%20and%20giving%20the%20option%20to%20the%20user%20to%20evaluate%20whether%20it%20is%20synthetic%20or%20natural%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20attended%20by%20representatives%20of%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20companies%20working%20on%20tools%20that%20can%20create%20AI-generated%20video%2C%20audio%20or%20images%2C%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Software%20and%20Service%20Companies%20(NASSCOM)%2C%20and%20professors%20working%20in%20the%20field%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20minister%20said%20all%20the%20attendees%20unanimously%20agreed%20that%20the%20issue%20should%20be%20addressed%20at%20the%20earliest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Big%20Concern'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20virtual%20G20%20Summit%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20called%20for%20a%20proper%20look%20into%20the%20lightning-fast%20growth%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20amid%20safety%20concerns%20and%20asked%20G20%20nations%20to%20work%20jointly%20on%20addressing%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20should%20reach%20people%2C%20and%20it%20must%20be%20safe%20for%20society...%20Deepfake%20is%20a%20big%20concern.%20AI%20has%20to%20be%20safe%20for%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20deepfake%20videos%20of%20actors%20Rashmika%20Mandhana%20and%20Katrina%20Kaif%20emerged%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20several%20celebrities%20had%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20misuse%20of%20AI%20and%20called%20for%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700727240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fum6k8aak_ashwini-vaishnaw_650x400_23_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-come-up-with-regulation-penalty-likely-for-creating-deepfakes-and-platforms-hosting-them-4598838%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20key%20meeting%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20deepfakes%2C%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20that%20the%20government%20and%20companies%20working%20in%20the%20Information%20Technology%20domain%20will%20bring%20out%20detailed%20guidelines%20on%20the%20detection%2C%20prevention%20and%20spread%20of%20such%20videos%20within%20ten%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-come-up-with-regulation-penalty-likely-for-creating-deepfakes-and-platforms-hosting-them-4598838%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-come-up-with-regulation-penalty-likely-for-creating-deepfakes-and-platforms-hosting-them-4598838%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-come-up-with-regulation-penalty-likely-for-creating-deepfakes-and-platforms-hosting-them-4598838%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mirror%2C%20Hong%20Kong%20Boy%20Band%2C%20Sets%20Dates%