0COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20now%20faces%20a%20new%20threat%3A%20a%20mysterious%20pneumonia%20outbreak%20sweeping%20through%20its%20educational%20institutions.%20With%20echoes%20of%20the%20harrowing%20scenes%20of%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20this%20new%20development%20has%20triggered%20a%20surge%20in%20hospital%20admissions%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Chinese%20health%20officials%20from%20the%20National%20Health%20Commission%20(NHC)%20convened%20a%20press%20conference%20to%20address%20a%20recent%20surge%20in%20respiratory%20illnesses%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESurge%20In%20Respiratory%20Diseases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20in%20China%20have%20linked%20the%20upsurge%20in%20respiratory%20illnesses%20to%20the%20easing%20of%20COVID-19%20restrictions%20and%20the%20reemergence%20of%20well-known%20pathogens%2C%20including%20influenza%2C%20mycoplasma%20pneumoniae%2C%20a%20widespread%20bacterial%20infection%20that%20typically%20affects%20younger%20children%2C%20respiratory%20syncytial%20virus%2C%20and%20the%20virus%20that%20causes%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%2C%20%26quot%3BMycoplasma%20pneumoniae%20bacteria%20commonly%20cause%20mild%20infections%20of%20the%20respiratory%20system%20(the%20parts%20of%20the%20body%20involved%20in%20breathing).%20Sometimes%20these%20bacteria%20can%20cause%20more%20serious%20lung%20infections%20that%20require%20care%20in%20a%20hospital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20undiagnosed%20pneumonia%20was%20not%20addressed%20at%20the%20NHC%20press%20conference%2C%20a%20closer%20examination%20of%20the%20transcript%20indicates%20that%20one%20speaker%20alluded%20to%20a%20perceptible%20increase%20in%20respiratory%20illnesses%20this%20year%20compared%20to%20three%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20is%20currently%20battling%20a%20relentless%20cold%20spell.%20State%20media%20reports%20predict%20that%20temperatures%20will%20nosedive%2C%20plunging%20far%20below%20freezing%20by%20Friday.%20The%20surge%20in%20respiratory%20infections%20has%20coincided%20with%20the%20city's%20recent%20plunge%20into%20frigid%20temperatures%2C%20Wang%20Quanyi%2C%20deputy%20director%20and%20chief%20epidemiological%20expert%20at%20the%20Beijing%20Center%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%2C%20told%20state%20media%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20%26quot%3Bis%20currently%20showing%20a%20trend%20of%20multiple%20pathogens%20coexisting%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20added%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHospitals%20Overflowing%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHospitals%20in%20Beijing%20and%20Liaoning%20are%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20collapse%20due%20to%20an%20overwhelming%20surge%20of%20sick%20children%2C%20reports%20claim.%20With%20the%20outbreak%20surging%2C%20school%20closures%20are%20also%20a%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20AFP%20reported%20a%20bustling%20scene%20at%20Beijing's%20Capital%20Institute%20of%20Pediatrics'%20Children's%20Hospital%2C%20where%20parents%20and%20children%2C%20clad%20in%20winter%20apparel%2C%20navigated%20the%20crowded%20corridors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20ProMED%2C%20a%20vigilant%20media%20and%20public%20disease%20surveillance%20system%2C%20flagged%20the%20presence%20of%20undiagnosed%20pneumonia%20clusters%20among%20children%20in%20northern%20China%2C%20prompting%20health%20authorities%20to%20investigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20ProMed%20alert%20issued%20in%20late%20December%202019%20served%20as%20an%20early%20warning%20signal%2C%20alerting%20the%20medical%20community%2C%20scientific%20world%2C%20and%20high-ranking%20officials%20at%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20to%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20novel%20virus%2C%20later%20identified%20as%20SARS-CoV-2%20or%20coronavirus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20outbreak%20of%20pneumonia%20in%20China%2C%20children's%20hospitals%20in%20Beijing%2C%20Liaoning%20and%20other%20places%20were%20overwhelmed%20with%20sick%20children%2C%20and%20schools%20and%20classes%20were%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20suspension.%20Parents%20questioned%20whether%20the%20authorities%20were%20covering%20up%20the%20epidemic%2C%26quot%3B%20ProMed%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20in%20Liaoning%20Province%20is%20also%20serious.%20The%20lobby%20of%20Dalian%20Children's%20Hospital%20is%20full%20of%20sick%20children%20receiving%20intravenous%20drips.%20There%20are%20also%20queues%20of%20patients%20at%20the%20traditional%20Chinese%20medicine%20hospitals%20and%20the%20central%20hospitals%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20WHO%20Said%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20has%20requested%20that%20China%20furnish%20more%20detailed%20data%2C%20while%20also%20issuing%20a%20public%20health%20advisory%20urging%20individuals%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20reduce%20their%20exposure%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWHO%20has%20made%20an%20official%20request%20to%20China%20for%20detailed%20information%20on%20an%20increase%20in%20respiratory%20illnesses%20and%20reported%20clusters%20of%20pneumonia%20in%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UN%20health%20body%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20the%20WHO%20repeatedly%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20openness%20and%20collaboration%20demonstrated%20by%20Chinese%20authorities%20in%20their%20handling%20of%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700726100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Ffv0oojco_china-coronavirus-afp_625x300_15_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-pneumonia-outbreak-explaine