2Ftwitter.com%2Fnishikant_dubey%2Fstatus%2F1727565969474937132%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20faces%20allegations%20of%20asking%20questions%20in%20Parliament%20in%20exchange%20for%20monetary%20benefits%20and%20gifts%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani.%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee%20has%20recently%20recommended%20her%20expulsion%20as%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Dubey%20wrote%20to%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%2C%20accusing%20Ms%20Moitra%20of%20accepting%20bribes%20from%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20targeting%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20business%20rival%20Adani%20Group.%20The%20Trinamool%20MP%20is%20also%20accused%20of%20sharing%20her%20Parliament%20login%20credentials%20with%20the%20businessman%20so%20that%20he%20could%20post%20questions%20on%20her%20behalf.%20Ms%20Moitra%20has%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20regulation%20regarding%20the%20sharing%20of%20login%20and%20password.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dubey%20shared%20shots%20from%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20bulletin%20sharing%20information%20%26quot%3Brelating%20to%20Parliamentary%20and%20other%20matters%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMembers%20are%20aware%20that%20under%20a%20new%20initiative%2C%20replies%20to%20Starred%20Questions%20are%20being%20uploaded%20on%20Members'%20Portal%20by%200900%20hours%20on%20the%20reply%20day.%20This%20initiative%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20facilitate%20Members%20to%20frame%20supplementaries.%20Similarly%2C%20replies%20to%20Unstarred%20Questions%20are%20being%20uploaded%20on%20Lok%20Sabha%20Homepage%20immediately%20after%20Question%20Hour%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20since%20the%20replies%20are%20login%20and%20password%20protected%20on%20the%20Members'%20Portal%2C%20they%20are%20exclusively%20for%20the%20use%20of%20Members%20only.%20Members%20are%2C%20therefore%2C%20requested%20to%20maintain%20confidentiality%20of%20the%20replies%20and%20not%20to%20share%20the%20contents%20with%20others%20until%20the%20Question%20Hour%20is%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20section%20on%20the%20confidentiality%20clause%20underlined%20that%20replies%20to%20oral%20questions%20are%20strictly%20confidential%20until%20the%20question%20has%20been%20actually%20answered%20in%20the%20House.%20%26quot%3BIn%20case%20the%20question%20has%20not%20reached%20for%20oral%20answer%2C%20the%20reply%20to%20the%20Question%20should%20not%20be%20released%20till%20the%20conclusion%20of%20Question%20Hour.%20Questions%20included%20in%20the%20lists%20of%20written%20answers%20are%20also%20to%20be%20treated%20as%20confidential%20until%20the%20same%20have%20been%20laid%20on%20the%20Table%20of%20the%20House%20after%20the%20Question%20Hour%20is%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20MP%20has%20probably%20not%20been%20briefed%20properly%20by%20a%20PA%20like%20Hiranandani%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20said%20in%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Krishnanagar%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hiranandani%20has%20admitted%20to%20using%20Ms%20Moitra's%20login%20credentials%20and%20called%20them%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%20error%20of%20judgment%20and%20deeply%20regrettable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700725800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fin6sfjg_mahua-moitra-pti_625x300_28_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnishikant-dubey-mahua-moitra-darshan-hiranandani-bjp-mps-chori-seenazori-barb-at-mahua-moitra-reads-out-lok-sabha-rules-4598922%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20fresh%20attack%20on%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20has%20cited%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20document%20that%20states%20that%20replies%20to%20questions%20asked%20by%20MPs%20must%20remain%20confidential%20till%20the%20questio