com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-tunnel-video-israel-displays-tunnel-under-gaza-hospital-it-claims-was-a-hamas-terror-complex-4598652%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Acres%2C%20Rs%20262%20Crore%2C%2010%2C000%20Capacity%3A%20Banke%20Bihari%20Temple%20Corridor%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20approved%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20special%20corridor%20for%20the%20Banke%20Bihari%20Temple%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Mathura.%20The%20temple%20corridor%2C%20to%20be%20built%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20Kashi-Vishwanath%20Temple%20Corridor%2C%20will%20offer%20devotees%20three%20convenient%20routes%20to%20reach%20the%20Krishna%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20of%20the%20historic%20corridor%20will%20cost%20Rs%20262%20crore%20which%20will%20be%20funded%20by%20the%20UP%20government.%20To%20be%20built%20over%205%20acres%2C%20over%2010%2C000%20devotees%20can%20stay%20inside%20the%20complex%20at%20a%20time.%20Devotees%20will%20be%20able%20reach%20the%20temple%20through%20three%20routes%20--%20from%20Jugalghat%2C%20Vidyapeeth%20intersection%20and%20from%20the%20Jadoun%20parking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20corridor%2C%20which%20will%20surround%20the%20temple%2C%20will%20have%20two%20floors.%20The%20ground%20floor%20of%20the%20entrance%20complex%20will%20be%20spread%20over%2011%2C300%20square%20meters.%20The%20ground%20floor%20will%20also%20house%20shops%20selling%20for%20puja%20items%20and%20include%20a%20corridor%20of%20Krishna%20paintings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20also%20be%20a%20%C2%A03.500%20square-metre%20waiting%20room%20built%20for%20pilgrims%20and%205%2C113%20square%20meters%20will%20be%20an%20open%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government's%20proposal%20for%20the%20corridor%20faced%20strong%20opposition%20from%20local%20residents%20who%20said%20they%20will%20be%20displaced%20or%20their%20daily%20lives%20will%20be%20disrupted%20by%20the%20project.%20Priests%20and%20shopkeepers%20also%20wrote%20letter%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20with%20their%20blood%2C%20requesting%20him%20to%20stop%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20a%20bench%20comprising%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20Pritinker%20Diwaker%20and%20Justice%20Ashutosh%20Srivastava%20gave%20approval%20for%20the%20UP%20government%20scheme%20proposing%20the%20new%20corridor.%20The%20state%20government%20ensured%20that%20the%20construction%20would%20not%20hinder%20the%20devotees%20while%20offering%20prayers%20at%20the%20Banke%20Bihari%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vrindavan%20temple%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20pilgrim%20sites%20in%20North%20India%20for%20Krishna%20devotees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20corridor%20is%20among%20many%20proposed%20to%20be%20built%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20across%20the%20country%20to%20boost%20religious%20tourism%20within%20India.%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20inaugurated%20the%20Mahakal%20Corridor%20last%20year%20at%20the%20Shri%20Mahakaleshwar%20Temple%20in%20%C2%A0Madhya%20Pradesh's%C2%A0Ujjain.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700725320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F09d4phu8_bak-bihari-temple-corridor_625x300_23_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbanke-bihari-corridor-5-acres-rs-262-crore-10-000-capacity-banke-bihari-temple-corridor-plan-4598977%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20approved%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20special%20corridor%20for%20the%20Banke%20Bihari%20Temple%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Mathura.%20The%20temple%20corridor%2C%20will%20be%20built%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20Kashi-Vishwanath%20Temple%20Corridor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbanke-bihari-corridor-5-acres-rs-262-crore-10-000-capacity-banke-bihari-temple-corridor-plan-4598977%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn