ruggle.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pinkvilla.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fexclusive-video-they-want-to-touch-you-ankit-gupta-opens-up-on-his-casting-couch-experience-1259819%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20to%20Pinkvilla%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ankit%20Gupta%20opened%20about%20having%20faced%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20casting%20couch%20early%20in%20his%20career.%20The%20actor%20said%20that%20several%20people%20would%20meet%20him%2C%20promise%20him%20job%20opportunities%20in%20return%20for%20favours.%20When%20asked%20if%20Ankit%20Gupta%20had%20ever%20faced%20the%20casting%20couch%20in%20his%20career%2C%20the%20star%20said%20with%20a%20wry%20smile%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20met%20such%20people%20that%20I%20can't%20even%20tell%20you.%20There%20are%20people%2C%20they%20call%20you%20with%20offers%2C%20and%20they%20tell%20you%20lots%20of%20stories%20and%20they%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20names%E2%80%A6%3Cem%3E%20usko%20mein%20banaya%2C%20isko%20mein%20launch%20kiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B%20I%20launched%20that%20person%5D%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20convince%20you%20they%20would%20say%20anything%3Cem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20what%20he%20was%20told%20by%20those%20engaging%20in%20such%20activities%2C%20Ankit%20Gupta%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Everybody%20does%20it%2C%20Ankit.%20You%20want%20to%20work%20in%20the%20industry%3F%20This%20is%20how%20it's%20done.%20%3Cem%3ETu%20abhi%20nahi%20karega%2C%202-3%20saal%20baad%20ayega%2C%20phir%20kahega%20aab%20kar%20lo%2C%20mein%20nahi%20karunga%20%3C%2Fem%3E(You%20are%20not%20doing%20it%20right%20now%2C%20but%20you%20will%20return%20after%20a%20few%20years%20and%20agree%20to%20do%20it%20then.)%20You%20don't%20wanna%20waste%202-3%20years.'%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20Gupta%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20met%20such%20people%E2%80%A6%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20should%20say%20this%20on%20camera%20or%20not%2C%20they%20would%20go%20down%20on%20their%20knees%20and%20say%2C%20at%20least%20let%20me%20touch%20you.%20That's%20it%2C%20nothing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20actor%20Shiv%20Thakare%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20a%20contestant%20alongside%20Ankit%20Gupta%20in%20%3Cem%3EBigg%20Boss%2016%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20also%20spoke%20about%20his%20casting%20couch%20experience%20in%20the%20industry.%20Sharing%20that%20the%20casting%20couch%20is%20a%20bane%20that%20does%20not%20discriminate%20between%20men%20and%20women%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftv%2Fshiv-thakare-recalls-being-called-to-a-massage-centre-under-the-pretext-of-auditions-ladkon-ko-bhi-dar-rehta-hai-exclusive-101680144544292.html%5C%22%3E%20Shiv%20Thakare%20told%20Hindustan%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20once%20went%20for%20an%20audition%20in%20Aram%20Nagar%20and%20he%20took%20me%20to%20the%20bathroom%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EYaha%20pe%20massage%20centre%20hai'.%3C%2Fem%3E%20I%20didn't%20get%20the%20connection%20between%20an%20audition%20and%20a%20massage%20centre.%20He%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EEk%20baar%20aap%20aao%20yaha%20audition%20ke%20baad.%20Aap%20workout%20bhi%20karte%20ho...%3C%2Fem%3E'%20I%20just%20left%20the%20place%2C%20since%20he%20was%20a%20casting%20director%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20take%20any%20pangas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20no%20Salman%20Khan.%20But%20I%20realised%20there%20is%20no%20discrimination%20between%20men%20and%20women%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20this%20(casting%20couch)%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20ma'am%20in%20Four%20Bungalows.%20She%20would%20tell%20me%20ki%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMaine%20isko%20banaya%20hai%2C%20maine%20usko%20banaya%20hai'.%3C%2Fem%3E%20She%20was%20calling%20me%20for%20an%20audition%20at%2011%20in%20the%20night%3Cem%3E.%20Itna%20bhola%20toh%20nahi%20hoon%20main%3C%2Fem%3E%20ki%20I%20won't%20understand%20what%20auditions%20happen%20at%20night.%20So%2C%20I%20told%20her%20that%20I%20have%20some%20work%20and%20I%20cannot%20make%20it.%20To%20this%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKaam%20nahi%20karna%3F'%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%98You%20won't%20get%20work%20in%20the%20industry'%20and%20other%20such%20things.%20So%2C%20they%20would%20demotivate%20you%20and%20manipulate%20you.%20But%20I%20would%20never%20get%20bothered%20by%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20echoing%20what%20Ankit%20Gupta%20would%20come%20to%20say%20several%20months%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20work%20front%2C%20Ankit%20Gupta%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20the%20TV%20show%20%3Cem%3EJunooniyatt%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700724840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fmriuqgp_ankit-_625x300_23_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fankit-gupta-opens-up-about-casting-couch-experience-i-have-met-such-people-that-i-can-t-even-tell-you-4598797%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ankit%20Gupta%20is%20known%20for%20his%20work%20in%20Udaariyan%20and%20Bigg%20Boss%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fankit-gupta-opens-up-about-casting-couch-experience-i-have-met-such-people-that-i-can-t-even-tell-you-4598797%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fankit-gupta-opens-up-about-casting-couch-experience-i-have-met-such-people-that-i-can-t-even-tell-you-4598797%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fankit-gupta-opens-up-about-casting-couch-experience-i-have-met-such-people-that-i-can-t-even-tell-you-4598797%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WI's%20T20%20WC-Winning%20Star%20Banned%20By%20ICC%20For%20Anti-Corruption%20Code%20Violation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20West%20Indies%20star%20batter%20Marlon%20Samuels%20on%20Thursday%20was%20banned%20from%20all%20cricket%20for%20six%20years%20after%20he%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20breaching%20the%20Emirates%20Cricket%20Board%20(ECB)%20Anti-Corruption%20Code.%20The%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20confirmed%20that%20%26quot%3BSamuels%20was%20charged%20by%20the%20ICC%20-%20in%20their%20capacity%20as%20the%20Designated%20Anti-Corruption%20Official%20under%20the%20ECB%20Code%20-%20on%20a%20total%20of%20four%20charges%20in%20September%202021%20and%20then%20found%20guilty%20of%20the%20offences%20in%20August%20this%20year.%20The%20ban%20of%20six%20years%20was%20confirmed%20by%20the%20ICC%20on%20Thursday%20and%20will%20commence%20from%20November%2011%2C%202023.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20charges%20that%20Samuel%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20are%20Article%202.4.2%20(by%20a%20majority%20decision)%20-%20Failing%20to%20disclose%20to%20the%20Designated%20Anti-Corruption%20Official%2C%20the%20receipt%20of%20any%20gift%2C%20payment%2C%20hospitality%20or%20other%20benefit%20that%20was%20made%20or%20given%20in%20circumstances%20that%20could%20bring%20the%20Participant%20or%20the%20sport%20of%20cricket%20into%20disrepute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%202.4.3%20(unanimous%20decision)-%20Failing%20to%20disclose%20to%20the%20Designated%20Anti-Corruption%20Official%20receipt%20of%20hospitality%20with%20a%20value%20of%20USD%20750%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%202.4.6%20(unanimous%20decision)%20-%20Failing%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20Designated%20Anti-Corruption%20Official's%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%202.4.7%20(unanimous%20decision)%20-%20Obstructing%20or%20delaying%20the%20Designated%20Anti-Corruption%20Official's%20investigation%20by%20concealing%20information%20that%20may%20have%20been%20relevant%20to%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20was%20announced%20on%20Thursday%20by%20Alex%20Marshall%20the%20head%20of%20ICC%20HR%20and%20Integrity%20Unit%2C%20and%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSamuels%20played%20international%20cricket%20for%20close%20to%20two%20decades%2C%20during%20which%20he%20participated%20in%20numerous%20anti-corruption%20sessions%20and%20knew%20exactly%20what%20his%20obligations%20were%20under%20the%20Anti-Corruption%20Codes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20he%20is%20retired%20now%2C%20Samuels%20was%20a%20participant%20when%20the%20offences%20were%20committed.%20The%20ban%20of%20six%20years%20will%20act%20as%20a%20strong%20deterrent%20to%20any%20participant%20who%20intends%20to%20break%20the%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20Marshall%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20career%20which%20lasted%20for%20over%2018%20years%2C%20Samuels%20featured%20in%20more%20than%20300%20matches%20for%20the%20West%20Indies%2C%20amassing%2017%20centuries%20in%20total.%20His%20illustrated%20career%20also%20saw%20him%20captain%20the%20Caribbean%20side%20in%20the%20ODI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20knocks%20of%2078%20and%2085*%2C%20Samuels%20was%20the%20top-scorer%20in%20the%20final%20of%20both%20the%202012%20and%202016%20editions%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20as%20the%20West%20Indies%20won%20their%20two%20most%20recent%20ICC%20trophies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700724600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F4kv11f08_west-indies-2012-t20-world-cup-afp_625x300_23_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwest-indies-t20-world-cup-winning-star-banned-by-icc-for-anti-corruption-code-violation-4598889%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ban%20of%20six%20years%20was%20confirmed%20by%20the%20ICC%20on%20Thursday%20and%20will%20commence%20from%20November%2011%2C%202023%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwest-indies-t20-world-cup-winning-star-banned-by-icc-for-anti-corruption-code-violation-4598889%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproj