F105437573.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Parineeti%20rejected%20'Animal%E2%80%99%20with%20Ranbir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700724507000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105438308%2Cimgsize-12968.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-heres-why-parineeti-chopra-opted-out-of-ranbir-kapoors-animal%2Farticleshow%2F105438349.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105438349.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EParineeti%20Chopra%2C%20a%20popular%20actress%2C%20was%20initially%20the%20first%20choice%20for%20the%20female%20lead%20in%20Ranbir%20Kapoor's%20action%20flick%20'Animal'.%20In%20a%20candid%20interview%20with%20India%20Today%2C%20she%20revealed%20that%20she%20opted%20out%20of%20the%20film%20in%20favor%20of%20Imtiaz%20Ali's%20upcoming%20project.%20This%20decision%20became%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20Chopra's%20career%2C%20as%20it%20showcased%20her%20inclination%20towards%20challenging%20roles%20that%20allowed%20her%20to%20explore%20different%20characters.%20Parineeti%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20directors%20Ribhu%20Dasgupta%20and%20Dibakar%20Banerjee%20for%20their%20instrumental%20roles%20in%20shaping%20her%20journey%20within%20the%20industry.%20She%20also%20has%20several%20highly%20anticipated%20projects%20in%20the%20pipeline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-heres-why-parineeti-chopra-opted-out-of-ranbir-kapoors-animal%2Farticleshow%2F105438349.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Non-Biology%20Class%2012%20Students%20Can%20Now%20Aspire%20To%20Become%20Doctors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStudents%20who%20have%20successfully%20completed%20their%2010%2B2%20examinations%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20physics%2C%20chemistry%2C%20and%20mathematics%2C%20can%20still%20aspire%20to%20become%20doctors.%20The%20new%20guidelines%20from%20the%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20(NMC)%20outline%20a%20pathway%20for%20such%20candidates.%20To%20qualify%2C%20they%20need%20to%20pass%20a%20biology%2Fbiotechnology%20examination%20as%20an%20additional%20subject%20at%20the%2010%2B2%20level%20from%20any%20recognised%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20public%20notice%20issued%20by%20the%20NMC%2C%20candidates%20who%20have%20included%20the%20necessary%20subjects-physics%2C%20chemistry%2C%20biology%2Fbiotechnology%2C%20and%20English-even%20as%20additional%20subjects%20after%20passing%20Class%2012%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20the%20NEET-UG%20test%20for%20admission%20to%20MBBS%20and%20BDS%20courses%20in%20the%20country.%20Additionally%2C%20these%20candidates%20will%20be%20eligible%20to%20receive%20an%20eligibility%20certificate%20from%20the%20NMC%2C%20a%20legal%20document%20confirming%20their%20eligibility%20to%20study%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20candidates%20were%20obligated%20to%20undergo%20two%20years%20of%20continuous%20study%20in%20physics%2C%20chemistry%2C%20biology%2Fbiotechnology%2C%20and%20English%2C%20including%20practicals%2C%20during%20Classes%2010%20and%2012%20to%20be%20eligible%20for%20MBBS%20or%20BDS%20programs.%20This%20two-year%20study%20had%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20a%20regular%20school%20and%20not%20through%20an%20open%20school%20or%20as%20a%20'private'%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20previous%20regulations%2C%20after%20passing%20Class%2012%2C%20students%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20take%20additional%20subjects%20and%20instead%20had%20to%20finish%20their%20studies%20in%20biology%2C%20biotechnology%2C%20or%20any%20other%20required%20subject%20as%20part%20of%20the%20core%20curriculum.%20This%20restriction%20has%20been%20lifted%20by%20the%20new%20NMC%20order%2C%20providing%20a%20path%20to%20medical%20school%20for%20individuals%20who%20wish%20to%20pursue%20it%20even%20if%20biology%20or%20biotechnology%20were%20not%20required%20in%20Classes%2011%20and%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NMC%20stated%20that%20discussions%20on%20this%20matter%20took%20place%20on%20June%2014%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20decision%20to%20relax%20the%20criteria%20for%20NEET-UG%20eligibility%20and%20the%20issuance%20of%20eligibility%20certificates%20for%20studying%20medicine%20abroad.%20This%20decision%20aligns%20with%20the%20flexibility%20introduced%20by%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%2C%20allowing%20a%20more%20adaptable%20approach%20to%20studying%20various%20subjects%20in%20Class%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700724180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-06%2Fdoctor-generic_650x400_41498064878.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnmc-opens-doors-for-non-biology-students-to-aspire-to-become-doctors-4598904%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NMC%20Guidelines%20For%20Non-Biology%20Students%3A%20To%20qualify%2C%20they%20need%20to%20pass%20a%20biology%2Fbiotechnology%20examination%20as%20an%20additional%20subject%20at%20the%2010%2B2%20level%20from%20any%20recognised%20board.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnmc-opens-doors-for-non-biology-students-to-aspire-to-become-doctors-4598904%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnmc-opens-doors-for-non-biology-students-to-aspire-to-become-doctors-4598904%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnmc-opens-doors-for-non-biology-students-to-aspire-to-become-doctors-4598904%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Contender%20%E2%80%982018%E2%80%99%20Director%20Talks%20Oscar%20Campaign%