om%2Findustry%2Fhealthcare%2Fbiotech%2Fpharmaceuticals%2Fdrug-regulator-halts-production-at-76-units-over-poor-standards%2Farticleshow%2F105425061.cms%23%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20poor%20manufacturing%20standards%20were%20discovered%20during%20risk-based%20inspections%20that%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20since%20December%2C%20people%20aware%20of%20the%20matter%20told%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20cited%20data%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECentral%20Drugs%20Standard%20Control%20Organisation%20(CDSCO)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20saying%20that%20out%20of%20the%20237%20manufacturing%20units%20that%20have%20been%20inspected%20so%20far%2C%20179%20have%20been%20issued%20show%20cause%20notices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELicences%20of%2015%20firms%20have%20been%20cancelled%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2015%25%20of%20the%20total%20samples%20drawn%20from%20these%20manufacturing%20units%20have%20been%20declared%20to%20be%20not%20of%20standard%20quality.%20And%20therefore%2C%2035%20units%20have%20been%20sent%20warning%20letters%20for%20discrepancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20regulator%20is%20currently%20conducting%20Phase%20IV%20of%20these%20inspections%2C%20during%20which%2051%20pharma%20firms%20have%20been%20inspected%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20inspections%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20CDSCO%20along%20with%20state%20drug%20inspectors%20after%20cough%20syrups%20manufactured%20in%20India%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fcough-syrup-india-gambia-deaths-children-who%5C%22%3Elinked%20to%20the%20deaths%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20more%20than%2060%20children%20in%20Gambia.%20This%20incident%20sparked%20serious%20concerns%20over%20the%20quality%20of%20Indian%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20299%20firms%2C%20including%2072%20private%20testing%20laborat