the%20three%20crew%20members%20%26quot%3Binvented%26quot%3B%20the%20armed%20robbery%20to%20avoid%20being%20punished%20by%20bosses.%20The%20cops%20said%20they%20found%20inconsistencies%20in%20their%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20in%20Brazil%20said%20one%20of%20the%20crimes%20the%20crew%20members%20talked%20about%20did%20happen%2C%20but%20the%20three%20went%20to%20an%20abandoned%20police%20station%20to%20take%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20field%20investigation%20and%20intelligence%20work%2C%20data%20crossing%20and%20image%20analysis%2C%20the%20Special%20Tourism%20Support%20Delegation%20(Deat)%20found%20that%20three%20flight%20attendants%20from%20an%20English%20company%2C%20who%20reported%20having%20been%20robbed%20in%20September%20this%20year%20lied%20in%20their%20testimony%20when%20recording%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Civil%20Police%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fcrime%2Fbritish-airways-rio-de-janeiro-b2448410.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20Deat%2C%20of%20the%20various%20crimes%20reported%20by%20the%20trio%2C%20only%20one%20occurred%2C%20after%20a%20late%20night%20in%20which%20they%20consumed%20drugs%20and%20alcohol%20and%20went%20to%20an%20abandoned%20gas%20station%2C%20close%20to%20a%20community%20in%20Rio%2C%20where%20they%20continued%20their%20drug%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20crew%20members%20are%20being%20investigated%20for%20falsely%20reporting%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F11%2F16%2Fnews%2Fbritish-airways-cabin-crew-lied-about-armed-robbery-to-cover-up-booze-drug-binge-report%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20crew%20members%20are%20accused%20of%20taking%20Class%20A%20drugs%20during%20their%20night%20of%20partying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20surprising%20is%20how%20a%20crew%20that%20has%20such%20an%20important%20role%20spends%20the%20whole%20night%20drinking%20and%20using%20drugs%2C%20knowing%20that%20the%20next%20day%20they%20would%20have%20the%20responsibility%20of%20taking%20care%20of%20dozens%20of%20people%20who%20would%20travel%20for%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20Patricia%20Alemany%2C%20Head%20of%20the%20Special%20Tourism%20Support%20Police%2C%20told%20local%20news%20outlet%20Globo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20also%20reviewed%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20that%20shows%20them%20near%20the%20fuel%20station%20at%204.50am%20(local%20time).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20Airways%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20that%20this%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20matter%20for%20the%20police%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20flight%20attendants%20involved%20%26quot%3Bwere%20not%20scheduled%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20flight.%20The%20airline%20did%20not%20explain%20why%20BA248%20was%20postponed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700722680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-12%2Fq2kgo138_british-airways-plane_625x300_28_December_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-airways-crew-accused-of-lying-about-robbery-to-cover-up-night-of-partying-4598872%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20in%20Brazil%20said%20one%20of%20the%20crimes%20the%20crew%20members%20talked%20about%20did%20happen%2C%20but%20the%20three%20went%20to%20an%20abandoned%20police%20station%20to%20take%20drugs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-airways-crew-accused-of-lying-about-robbery-to-cover-up-night-of-partying-4598872%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-airways-crew-accused-of-lying-about-robbery-to-cover-up-night-of-partying-4598872%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com