s%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20board%20warning%20about%20a%20new%20AI%20algorithm%20called%20Q*%20that%20could%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20humanity.%20The%20algorithm%2C%20capable%20of%20solving%20certain%20math%20problems%20at%20a%20grade-school%20level%2C%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20by%20some%20members%20of%20OpenAI.%20The%20letter%20and%20discovery%20of%20the%20AI%20model%20were%20factors%20that%20led%20to%20Altman's%20dismissal%2C%20with%20concerns%20about%20hastened%20commercialization%20and%20safety.%20After%20Altman's%20firing%2C%20over%20700%20staff%20members%20threatened%20to%20resign%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20reinstatement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ABHINAV%20KAUSTUBH%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fproject-q-star-chatgpt-maker-openai-researchers-reportedly-warned-board-of-ai-breakthrough-that-can-threaten-humanity-ahead-of-sam-altmans-sacking%2Farticleshow%2F105436848.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20WC%20Final%20Loss%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav's%20Honest%20%26quot%3BIt%20Will%20Take%20Time%26quot%3B%20Revelation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%20is%20excited%20to%20captain%20India%20in%20the%20T20s%20against%20Australia%20but%20says%20it%20will%20take%20time%20to%20move%20on%20from%20the%20heartbreaking%20loss%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%20three%20days%20ago.%20The%20scheduling%20in%20international%20cricket%20is%20such%20that%20both%20India%20and%20Australia%20will%20return%20to%20the%20field%20in%20the%20opening%20game%20of%20the%20five-match%20T20%20series%20starting%20here%20on%20Thursday%2C%20albeit%20with%20a%20different%20set%20of%20players%2C%2096%20hours%20after%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20Surya%2C%20who%20could%20have%20done%20more%20in%20India's%20near-perfect%20campaign%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20was%20expectedly%20asked%20about%20the%20ill-fated%20Sunday%20night%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20T20%20series%20opener.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20difficult%20it%20will%20take%20time%2C%20it%20can't%20be%20that%20you%20wake%20up%20next%20morning%20and%20you%20forget%20everything%20what%20happened.%20It%20was%20a%20long%20tournament.%20We%20would%20have%20loved%20to%20win%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Surya%2C%20who%20will%20lead%20the%20side%20in%20Hardik%20Pandya's%20absence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20as%20you%20get%20up%20in%20the%20morning%20the%20sun%20rises%20again%2C%20there%20is%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel.%20You%20have%20to%20move%20on.%20It%20is%20a%20fresh%20team%20(T20%20squad)%2C%20really%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20challenge.%26quot%3B%20Surya%20said%20support%20from%20the%20fans%20and%20families%20is%20helping%20him%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20players%20to%20move%20on%20from%20the%20disappointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20a%20little%20disappointing%20but%20when%20you%20look%20back%20at%20the%20journey%20it%20was%20a%20great%20campaign.%20All%20of%20India%20and%20our%20families%20were%20proud%20about%20the%20way%20everyone%20displayed%20their%20talent%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20played%20a%20positive%20brand%20of%20cricket%20throughout%20the%20tournament.%20We%20can%20be%20very%20proud%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20aggressive%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20the%20game%20changer%20for%20India%20with%20the%20bat%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20as%20his%20explosive%20starts%20helped%20the%20team%20win%20a%20record%2010%20games%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Rohit)%20has%20set%20the%20example.%20It%20was%20a%20completely%20different%20Rohtit%20Sharma%2C%20he%20walked%20the%20talk.%20What%20we%20talked%20about%20in%20team%20meetings%20he%20did%20the%20same%20thing%20in%20the%20ground.%20We%20are%20very%20proud%20of%20him%2C%20he%20led%20by%20example%20and%20hopefully%20we%20will%20replicate%20that%20(in%20the%20T20s)%2C%26quot%3B%20Surya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20K%20L%20Rahul%20are%20not%20part%20of%20the%20squad%20having%20played%20their%20last%20T20%20match%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20T20%20squad%20is%20full%20of%20IPL%20performers%20who%20are%20yet%20to%20prove%20themselves%20at%20the%20highest%20level.%20The%20likes%20of%20Rinku%20Singh%2C%20who%20made%20his%20debut%20in%20Ireland%20and%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20Asian%20Games%2C%20and%20Tilak%20Varma%2C%20will%20face%20their%20toughest%20test%20in%20international%20cricket%20against%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20met%20the%20squad%20in%20the%20afternoon%20today.%20I%20told%20them%20lets%20be%20selfless%20when%20you%20go%20on%20to%20the%20field.%20I%20am%20a%20guy%20who%20doesn't%20think%20about%20personal%20milestones.%20I%20have%20told%20them%20to%20keep%20the%20team%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Surya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKeeping%20the%20(2024)%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20mind%2C%20all%20the%20games%20we%20are%20going%20to%20play%20are%20very%20important.%20I%20want%20us%20to%20be%20fearless.%26quot%3B%20Who%20among%20Jitesh%20Sharma%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan%20will%20be%20the%20designated%20wicket-keeper%20batter%20in%20the%20team%3F%20%26quot%3BIshan%20has%20been%20doing%20well%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20keep%20continuity.%20He%20has%20been%20doing%20really%20well%20for%20us%2C%20including%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20World%20Cup%2C%20batting%20in%20different%20positions.%20Both%20of%20them%20are%20front%20runners.%20We%20will%20take%20a%20call%20tonight%2C%26quot%3B%20Surya%20said%20with%20a%20laugh.%20PTI%20BS%20SSC%20SSC%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700721900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F3m6shh4g_c_625x300_22_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-tour-of-india-2023%2Fon-cricket-world-cup-2023-f