n%20tickets%20were%20on%20the%20waitlist%2C%20and%20the%20author%20eventually%20decided%20to%20travel%20by%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uber%20driver%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20was%20polite%20and%20had%20a%204.93%20rating%20on%20the%20app.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20daughter%20showed%20some%20signs%20of%20motion%20sickness%2C%20he%20voluntarily%20stopped%20the%20cab%20before%20a%20chemist%20for%20me%20to%20buy%20some%20medicines%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20sharing%20his%20first%20impressions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20was%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20driver%20talking%20over%20the%20phone%20while%20driving%2C%20but%20decided%20not%20to%20get%20into%20an%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Aftermath%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20truck%20driver%20fled%20without%20checking%20on%20us.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWe%20got%20out%20of%20the%20car%20and%20walked%20to%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20road%20to%20take%20stock.%20My%20daughter%20had%20a%20bruise%20on%20her%20right%20leg.%20She%20saw%20that%20I%20was%20in%20tremendous%20pain%20and%20kept%20calm%20for%20she%20knew%20that%20her%20panic%20would%20add%20to%20my%20woes.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fn6jTARUWCv%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fn6jTARUWCv%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dhaval%20Kulkarni%20(%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A3%E0%A5%80)%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40dhavalkulkarni)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdhavalkulkarni%2Fstatus%2F1727237856756973845%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSoon%20after%20we%20took%20the%20Expressway%2C%20the%20driver%20began%20yawning.%20He%20also%20drove%20rashly%20at%20times%2C%20cut%20lanes%2C%20and%20almost%20brushed%20against%20a%20truck.%20I%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20was%20sleepy%20or%20drowsy%20-