20passionate%20about%20her%20craft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInterior%20design%20is%20very%20creative%20and%20very%20cerebral.%20And%20that's%20the%20juxtaposition%20I%20was%20looking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gomez's%20last%20post%20on%20Instagram%20was%20on%20October%2023.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20future%20version%20of%20you%20that%20is%20so%20proud%20you%20didn't%20give%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700717460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F87c661j8_brooke-gomez_625x300_23_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finterior-designer-dead-at-49-body-found-decomposing-at-home-4598625%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20New%20York%20Police%20said%20that%20they%20don't%20suspect%20any%20criminality%20at%20this%20time%20in%20the%20death%20of%20interior%20designer%20Brooke%20Gomez.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finterior-designer-dead-at-49-body-found-decomposing-at-home-4598625%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finterior-designer-dead-at-49-body-found-decomposing-at-home-4598625%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finterior-designer-dead-at-49-body-found-decomposing-at-home-4598625%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Unconstitutionality%20of%20'Bulldozer%20Justice'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F16172609%2FUntitled-design-2021-07-16T172559.085.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Cbulldozer%20justice%E2%80%9D%20has%20come%20to%20describe%20a%20somewhat%20recurrent%20series%20of%20events%20that%20start%20with%20a%20communal%20clash%2C%20protest%2C%20or%20violence%20somewhere%2C%20and%20end%20with%20the%20demolition%20of%20homes%20in%20mostly%20Muslim%20neighborhoods%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20zoning%20regulations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20real%20intentions%20behind%20these%20demolitions%20are%20often%20poorly%20hidden%2C%20with%20many%20politicians%20and%20police%20officers%20openly%20stating%20that%20the%20drives%20were%20conducted%20to%20bring%20speedy%20justice%20to%20those%20who%20preempted%2C%20participated%20in%2C%20or%20organised%20the%20violence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20drive%20then%20becomes%20a%20way%20to%20secure%20justice%20%E2%80%93%20outside%20the%20law%20%E2%80%93%20for%20those%20who%20are%20perceived%20to%20be%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvictims%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20violence%20and%20the%20demolitions%20are%20carried%20out%20as%20extrajudicial%20punishment%20on%20those%20who%20are%20perceived%20to%20be%20its%20%E2%80%9Cperpetrators%E2%80%9D.%20Who%20these%20usual%20suspects%20are%20can%20be%20clearly%20deduced%20from%20the%20sites%20of%20these%20demolition%20drives%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20conversation%20on%20such%20%E2%80%9Cdemolition%20drives%E2%80%9D%20took%20off%20in%202022%20when%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fhow-the-jahangirpuri-demolition-destroyed-lives-of-indias-poorest-women%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENorth%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Corporation%20started%20razing%20houses%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Muslim%20localities%20following%20the%20communal%20clashes%20that%20shook%20Delhi%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20more%20recent%20phenomenon%20would%20be%20the%20demolitions%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20Muslim%20majority%20district%20of%20Mewat%20where%20houses%20(mostly%20belonging%20to%20Rohingya%20Muslims)%20in%20Nuh%20were%20similarly%20bulldozed%20after%20the%20communal%20clashes%20that%20took%20place%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnuh-demolitions-residents-due-process-damages%5C%22%3ENuh%20Demolitions%3A%20Residents%20Say%20Due%20Process%20Flouted%2C%20Reject%20%E2%80%98Illegal%20Establishments%E2%80%99%20Claim%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20government%20has%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20constructions%E2%80%9D%20were%20the%20primary%20reason%20for%20the%20demolitions%2C%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20court%20called%20the%20bluff%20by%20openly%20asking%20whether%20such%20acts%20were%20an%20%E2%80%9Cexercise%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing%E2%80%9D.%20The%20court%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fethnic-cleansing-by-state-punjab-and-haryana-hc-questions-nuh-demolitions-11691491070649.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobserved%20in%20an%20order%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Ct%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20issue%20also%20arises%20whether%20the%20buildings%20belonging%20to%20a%20particular%20community%20are%20being%20brought%20down%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20law-and-order%20problem%20and%20an%20exercise%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing%20is%20being%20conducted%20by%20the%20State%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20high%20court%20was%20alluding%20to%20also%20becomes%20relevant%20when%20we%20look%20at%20the%20timing%2C%20location%20and%20other%20characteristics%20of%20these%20demolitions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERight%20to%20adequate%20housing%20and%20due%20process%20of%20law%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20jurisprudence%20on%20the%20right%20to%20housing%20is%20well%20established%20under%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%2C%20multiple%20times%2C%20held%20the%20right%20to%20adequate%20housing%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20life%20under%20Article%2021.%20The%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20in%20the%20case%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F709776%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EOlga%20Tellis%20vs%20Bombay%20Municipal%20Corporation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3Efurther%20reiterates%20that%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20dignity%20and%20livelihood%20should%20be%20kept%20in%20mind%20while%20serving%20them%20with%20an%20eviction%20notice.%20The%20person%20being%20evicted%20must%20be%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20be%20heard.%20They%20must%20have%20the%20right%20to%20explain%20their%20situation%20to%20the%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20evictions%20must%20also%20follow%20the%20due%20process.%20The%20top%20court%20held%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F124752528%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMunicipal%20Corporation%20of%20Greater%20Mumbai%20%26amp%3B%20Ors.%20v%20M%2FS%20Sunbeam%20High%20Tech%20Developers%20Private%20Ltd%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20all%20evictions%20and%20demolitions%20must%20be%20in%20conformity%20with%20the%20law%20and%20the%20procedures%20established%20by%20law.%20The%20issuance%20of%20notice%20becomes%20an%20important%20part%20of%20due%20process%2C%20because%20it%20informs%20the%20citizen%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20allows%20them%20to%20either%20contest%20the%20demolition%20or%20gives%20them%20reasonable%20time%20to%20look%20for%20alternative%20accommodation.%C2%A0%20This%20right%20to%20a%20show-cause%20notice%20was%20held%20to%20be%20mandatory%20by%20a%202010%20Delhi%20high%20court%20judgement%20in%20the%20case%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F176799500%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBal%20Kishan%20Das%20vs%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20courts%20have%20gone%20one%20step%20further%20in%20ensuring%20the%20rights%20of%20those%20evicted%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F39539866%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESudama%20Singh%20%26amp%3B%20Others%20vs%20Government%20of%20Delhi%20%26amp%3B%20Anr%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20where%20it%20held%20that%20those%20who%20have%20gotten%20evicted%20by%20the%20authorities%20must%20be%20provided%20with%20housing%20equipped%20with%20basic%20amenities%20that%20help%20protect%20the%20citizens%20right%20to%20life%20and%20dignity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20many%20of%20those%20who%20have%20faced%20demolition%20drives%2C%20report%20being%20suddenly%20thrown%20out%20of%20their%20houses%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20with%20their%20houses%20or%20temporary%20shacks%20being%20destroyed%20along%20with%20all%20their%20belongings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20most%20cases%2C%20residents%20do%20not%20get%20a%20show-cause%20notice%20informing%20them%20of%20the%20demolition%20or%20if%20they%20do%2C%20they%20get%20it%20too%20late.%20They%20are%20not%20provided%20with%20any%20alternative%20accommodations%20and%20are%20left%20homeless%20as%20a%20result.%20Such%20instances%20of%20instant%20demolitions%20are%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20due%20process%20that%20has%20been%20laid%20down%20in%20multiple%20supreme%20court%20judgements%20and%20in%20legislations%20such%20as%20the%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Corporation%20Act%2C%201957.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERule%20of%20law%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20let%20us%20argue%20that%20the%20demolitions%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20with%20due%20process.%20This%20means%20that%20all%20those%20whose%20houses%20were%20demolished%20were%20served%20with%20notices%20well%20in%20advance%20and%20were%20given%20the%20right%20to%20be%20heard%20and%20provided%20with%20alternative%20accommodation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWould%20the%20inherent%20problem%20with%20these%20demolition%20drives%20cease%20to%20exist%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20no.%20The%20mere%20act%20of%20demolishing%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20structures%E2%80%9D%20is%20not%20in%20question%20here.%20We%20also%20need%20to%20look%20at%20the%20context%20around%20and%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20leading%20up%20to%20these%20demolitions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08154033%2Fimage4.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08154033%2Fimage4.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08154033%2Fimage4-300x210.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08154033%2Fimage4-1024x717.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667202%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMedicine%20supply%20stores%20and%20pathology%20labs%20reduced%20to%20debris%20near%20SHKM%20college%20at%20Nalhar.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECommunal%20violence%20leading%20to%20the%20state%20identifying%20%E2%80%9Cperpetrators%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20violence%20and%20then%20using%20bulldozers%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eilaaj%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20(treatment)%20to%20demolish%20their%20houses.%20All%20these%20circumstances%20have%20lead%20to%20India%20becoming%20a%20land%20with%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rule%20by%20law%20as%20opposed%20to%20rule%20of%20law%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EA.V.%20Dicey%20was%20a%20constitutional%20jurist%20in%2018th%20century%20Britain%20who%20popularised%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98rule%20of%20law%E2%80%99.%20The%20rule%20indicates%20that%20no%20one%20is%20above%20the%20law%20and%20that%20the%20law%20should%20be%20equally%20applied%20to%20everyone.%20The%20primary%20purpose%20behind%20the%20equal%20application%20of%20the%20law%20is%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20the%20influence%20of%20arbitrary%20power%20on%20it.%20This%20purpose%2C%20conversely%2C%20gets%20defeated%20if%20the%20law%20is%20applied%20unequally%20and%20selectively%20by%20those%20in%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDicey%E2%80%99s%20rule%20of%20law%20talked%20about%20a%20system%20of%20governance%20led%20by%20the%20concerns%20and%20issues%20faced%20by%20the%20citizens.%20The%20state%20would%20come%20in%20and%20use%20the%20law%20to%20find%20solutions%20to%20those%20problems.%20However%2C%20instances%20like%20the%20current%20demolition%20drives%20tell%20a%20different%20story.%20The%20rule%20of%20law%20is%20very%20clearly%20being%20changed%20to%20rule%20by%20law%20here%20because%20it%20seems%20the%20government%20and%20a%20few%20state%20actors%20are%20openly%20using%20the%20law%20to%20punish%20whoever%20they%20want.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20also%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20principles%20of%20constitutionalism%20which%20seek%20to%20limit%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20state%20and%20prevent%20the%20arbitrary%20application%20of%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZoning%20laws%20and%20laws%20related%20to%20city%20planning%20have%20always%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20anti-poor.%20They%20are%20the%20colonial%20remnants%20of%20the%20past%20where%20the%20colonial%20government%20would%20frequently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eraze%20over%20the%20native%E2%80%99s%20houses%20in%20order%20to%20build%20proper%20and%20%E2%80%9Cclean%E2%80%9D%20neighbourhoods%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20case%20is%20a%20stark%20example%20of%20the%20continuing%20colonial%20legacy%20where%20houses%20in%20affluent%20neighbourhoods%20are%20rarely%20targeted%20for%20non-compliance%20with%20zoning%20laws%20but%20poor%20households%20in%20mostly%20Muslim%20neighbourhoods%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiaforum.in%2Flaw%2Fdemolitions-rule-law-or-rule-law%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20often%20find%20themselves%20being%20targeted%20for%20such%20non-compliance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDemolitions%20as%20state-sponsored%20punishment%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20that%20we%20have%20assessed%20the%20problem%2C%20we%20must%20also%20learn%20to%20phrase%20and%20identify%20it%20in%20constitutional%20terms.%20The%20issue%20with%20that%20is%20that%20the%20constitutional%20courts%20when%20dealing%20with%20issues%20of%20illegal%20demolitions%20often%20treat%20them%20as%20individual%20cases%20and%20not%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20informal%20policy%20used%20by%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20problem%20to%20be%20fully%20recognised%2C%20we%20must%20learn%20to%20recognise%20demolition%20drives%20targeting%20neighbourhoods%20right%20after%20some%20clash%20or%20violence%20as%20a%20state-sponsored%20punishment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20where%20legal%20scholar%20Dr.%20Gautam%20Bhatia%20looks%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findconlawphil.wordpress.com%2F2022%2F06%2F12%2Fresponding-to-illegal-home-demolitions-the-doctrine-of-an-unconstitutional-state-of-affairs%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDoctrine%20of%20Unconstitutional%20Affairs%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20originated%20in%20Columbia%20and%20was%20later%20adopted%20by%20Brazil.%20As%20per%20a%20definition%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20unconstitutional%20state%20of%20affairs%20is%20a%20legal%20ruling%20that%20allows%20the%20Constitutional%20Court%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20failure%20of%20both%20the%20Legislative%20and%20Executive%20branches%20of%20government%20to%20enforce%20public%20policies%20against%20widespread%20and%20systemic%20violation%20of%C2%A0fundamental%20rights%2C%20thus%20justifying%20a%20judicial%20intervention%20in%20order%20to%20combat%20the%C2%A0structural%20causes%C2%A0of%20the%20violations%20and%20to%20put%20everything%20back%20in%20order%20with%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhatia%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F671023%2Fdemolitions-as-tools-of-collective-punishment-examining-instances-in-india-and-israel%2F%5C%22%3EDemolitions%20as%20Tools%20of%20%E2%80%98Collective%20Punishment%E2%80%99%3A%20Examining%20Instances%20in%20India%20and%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20doctrine%20focuses%20on%20the%20structural%20and%20systemic%20violation%20of%20fundamental%20rights.%20Using%20the%20doctrine%2C%20the%20courts%20will%20have%20to%20analyse%20and%20freely%20explore%20the%20patterns%20that%20lead%20to%20the%20bulldozing%20of%20houses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20systemic%20nature%20of%20these%20violations%20will%20then%20be%20scrutinised%20explicitly%20instead%20of%20an%20individual%20assessment%20of%20demolitions%20that%20views%20these%20incidents%20in%20Delhi%20(2022)%20and%20Haryana%20(2023)%20as%20isolated%20from%20each%20other.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20courts%20must%20step%20up%20to%20the%20challenge%20and%20learn%20to%20identify%20the%20problem%20of%20state%20sanctioned%20punishment%20before%20dealing%20with%20it.%20The%20religious%20profiling%20and%20gentrification%20of%20neighbourhoods%20being%20done%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20zoning%20laws%20and%20city%20planning%20will%20have%20to%20be%20talked%20about%20explicitly.%20This%20may%20be%20the%20only%20way%20to%20prevent%20the%20active%20ghettoization%20of%20marginalised%20communities%20and%20the%20gatekeeping%20of%20neighbourhoods%20around%20us.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20we%20are%20to%20uphold%20values%20of%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20constitutionalism%2C%20we%20must%20also%20curb%20the%20power%20of%20the%20state%20to%20arbitrarily%20disrupt%20the%20lives%20of%20those%20who%20it%20considers%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cguilty%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVarishtha%20Singh%20is%20a%20student%20of%20law%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700717441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F16172609%2FUntitled-design-2021-07-16T172559.085.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-unconstitutionality-of-bulldozer-justice%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20real%20intentions%20behind%20these%20demolitions%20are%20often%20poorly%20hidden%2C%20with%20many%20politicians%20and%20police%20officers%20openly%20stating%20that%20the%20drives%20were%20conducted%20to%20bring%20speedy%20justice%20to%20those%20who%20preempted%2C%20participated%20in%2C%20or%20organised%20purported%20violence.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-unconstitutionality-of-bulldozer-justice%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDeepfake%20A%20Big%20Issue%26quot%3B%3A%20IT%20Minister%20To%20Chair%20Key%20Meeting%20On%20AI%20Tech%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20proactive%20move%20to%20tackle%20the%20growing%20threat%20of%20deepfake%20technology%2C%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20and%20Communications%2C%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%2C%20is%20set%20to%20chair%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20today.%20The%20meeting%2C%20expected%20to%20be%20attended%20by%20Secretary%20MEITY%2C%20government%20officials%2C%20and%20cybersecurity%20experts%2C%20aims%20to%20strategize%20and%20address%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20deepfake%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20follows%20the%20Union%20Minister's%20announcement%20on%20November%2018%2C%20where%20he%20disclosed%20that%20notices%20had%20been%20issued%20to%20all%20major%20social%20media%20platforms.%20The%20notices%20directed%20these%20platforms%20to%20take%20immediate%20and%20effective%20measures%20to%20identify%20and%20remove%20deepfake%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20deepfake%20issue%20during%20a%20media%20interaction%20on%20November%2018%2C%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20emphasized%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20problem.%20He%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BDeepfake%20is%20a%20big%20issue%20for%20all%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20acknowledged%20the%20responsiveness%20of%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20the%20issued%20notices%2C%20expressing%20that%20they%20are%20actively%20taking%20steps%20to%20address%20the%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20urged%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20adopt%20a%20more%20aggressive%20approach%20in%20countering%20deepfake%20content.%20He%20emphasized%20that%20the%20'Safe%20Harbour'%20Clause%2C%20which%20has%20traditionally%20shielded%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20may%20not%20apply%20if%20they%20fail%20to%20take%20adequate%20measures%20against%20deepfakes%20on%20their%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Safe%20Harbour%20Clause%20that%20most%20of%20the%20social%20media%20platforms%20have%20been%20enjoying%20doesn't%20apply%20if%20the%20platforms%20do%20not%20take%20adequate%20steps%20to%20remove%20the%20deepfakes%20from%20their%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20meeting%2C%20led%20by%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20delve%20into%20comprehensive%20strategies%20for%20identifying%2C%20combating%2C%20and%20removing%20deepfake%20content.%3C%2F