Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20too%20in%20a%20stadium%20named%20after%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20invincible%20leader%2C%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20this%20happened%20in%20an%20arena%20named%20after%2C%20let%20us%20say%2C%20a%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20or%20such-like%2C%20the%20hurt%20may%20not%20have%20been%20so%20piquant%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20a%20time%20when%20India%20was%20a%20loser%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20great%20is%20the%20crestfallen%20grieving%20that%20many%20go%20hungry%20to%20bed%2C%20although%2C%20thankfully%2C%20there%20are%20no%20killer%20aircraft%20on%20their%20way%20to%20relieve%20the%20hunger%20with%20death%2C%20as%20they%20do%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20the%20woe%2C%20that%20our%20own%20flamboyant%20flypast%2C%20done%20in%20the%20sure%20antecedent%20knowledge%20that%20victory%20would%20be%20ours%2C%20were%20a%20waste%20of%20aviation%20turbo%20fuel%2C%20merely%20making%20noise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hush%20in%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20Pleased%20Cummins%20but%20it%20Diminished%20India%20in%20the%20Eyes%20of%20the%20World%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-cricket-world-cup-2023-final-pradeep-magazine%5C%22%3EHush%20in%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20Pleased%20Cummins%20but%20it%20Diminished%20India%20in%20the%20Eyes%20of%20the%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20the%20old-fashioned%20fools%20who%20still%20think%20cricket%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20a%20game%2C%E2%80%9D%20like%20hockey%20or%20football%2C%20or%20kabaddi%2C%20or%20archery%20which%20invite%20no%20flypast%2C%20only%20some%20joy%20in%20the%20hinterland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20Indians%20whom%20our%20great%20leap%20forward%20from%202014%20has%20left%20behind%2C%20like%20remnants%20of%20some%20mere%20family%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20do%20not%20mind%20losing%20this%20or%20that%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20even%20advocating%20that%20an%20occasional%20fall%20makes%20the%20soul%20more%20upright.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20of%20course%2C%20know%20there%20are%20only%20two%20kinds%20of%20people%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20the%20winners%20and%20the%20losers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20after%20interminable%20years%20of%20philosophising%2C%20thank%20Lord%20Ram%20that%20we%20are%20now%20among%20the%20winners%2C%20applauding%20kindred%20unrelenting%20winners%20like%20Israel%20in%20the%20teeth%20of%20apologetic%20legal%20and%20ethical%20hogwash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20win%20must%20mean%20to%20win%20at%20any%20cost%2C%20be%20it%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20cricket%20or%20politics%2C%20one%20and%20the%20same%20thing%20actually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20here%20is%20the%20worrying%20poser%3A%20how%20could%20we%20lose%20so%20abjectly%20in%20a%20colosseum%20that%20bears%20the%20name%20of%20the%20ever%20victorious%20%3Cem%3Eyodha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Modi%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20you%20know%20that%20even%20our%20beloved%20armed%20contingents%20like%20the%20CRPF%20etc.%20had%20fervently%20and%20publicly%20prayed%20(duly%20displayed%20on%20national%20television)%20for%20a%20national%20triumph%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20it%20is%20unendurable%20that%20our%20so-propitiated%20gods%20should%20have%20turned%20a%20deaf%20ear%20even%20to%20our%20all-conquering%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20enough%2C%20there%20will%20be%20vengeful%20mavericks%2C%20enemies%20of%20the%20sanatan%2C%20who%20will%20demand%20that%20the%20name%20of%20the%20stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%20be%20changed%2C%20just%20as%20many%20other%20inauspicious%20names%20of%20our%20tepid%20past%20continue%20to%20be%20supplanted%20by%20our%20contemporary%20history%E2%80%99s%20winners%2C%20be%20they%20names%20of%20streets%2C%20or%20buildings%2C%20or%20monuments%2C%20or%20days%20in%20the%20calendar%2C%20or%2C%20indeed%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20republic%20itself%20which%20has%20lately%20come%20to%20be%20desecrated%20by%20the%20political%20opposition%20who%20call%20themselves%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20contest%20of%20the%20day%20itself%2C%20was%20there%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20lay%20a%20pitch%20low%20and%20mean%20so%20as%2C%20ostensibly%2C%20to%20neuter%20the%20Aussie%20firing%20machine%20of%20hurlers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20it%20thought%20that%20just%20as%20the%20low%20and%20the%20mean%20have%20been%20so%20successful%20in%20the%20republic%E2%80%99s%20political%20life%2C%20it%20would%20be%20so%20in%20cricket%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%20was%20a%20treacherous%20ploy%20engineered%20by%20Modi-baiters%20in%20exchange%20for%20favours%20to%20this%20or%20that%20saboteur%2C%20posing%20as%20a%20groundsman%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20should%20not%20all%20other%20high-level%20investigations%20now%20underway%20be%20suspended%20so%20that%20the%20real%20culprits%20in%20this%20oh-so-humiliating%20snub%20be%20first%20looked%20into%20and%20the%20culprits%20duly%20hung%2C%20drawn%20and%20quartered%2C%20so%20that%20no%20World%20Cup%20is%20ever%20lost%20again%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Indian%20Cricket%20Team%20Was%20Burdened%20By%20the%20Weight%20of%20a%20Nation%20Which%20Always%20Wants%20to%20Be%20a%20Winner%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-cricket-team-winner%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Cricket%20Team%20Was%20Burdened%20By%20the%20Weight%20of%20a%20Nation%20Which%20Always%20Wants%20to%20Be%20a%20Winner%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20least%20ragamuffin%20citizen%20is%20convinced%20that%20the%20holy%20grail%20belongs%20to%20that%20which%20is%20sanatan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20the%20US%20were%20to%20lose%20a%20baseball%20series%20to%20Japan%2C%20as%20friendly%20a%20country%20to%20them%20as%20Australia%20to%20us%3B%20would%20not%20the%20president%20there%20order%20a%20no-holds-barred%20enquiry%20by%20the%20justice%20department%20into%20the%20perfidy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%2C%20if%20Donald%20Trump%20were%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20also%20be%20those%20so-called%20patriotic%20diplomats%2C%20in%20reality%20leftists%20moles%20in%20the%20foreign%20office%2C%20who%20might%20now%20advocate%20Bharat%E2%80%99s%20exit%20from%20the%20Quad%20as%20a%20first%20diplomatic%20protest%20action%20against%20the%20Australians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20if%20our%20everywhere-prime%20minister%20does%20not%20have%20enough%20on%20his%2024%C3%977%20plate%20in%20terms%20of%20righting%20interminable%20wrongs%20left%20over%20by%20decrepit%20Congress%20regimes%20of%20old%2C%20counselling%20short-sighted%20world%20figures%20to%20take%20a%20deep%20breath%20at%20their%20woes%20and%20enhancing%20the%20global%20good%20by%20being%20all%20things%20to%20all%20sides%2C%20be%20they%20Israelis%20or%20trouble-making%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20of%20the%20players%20who%20lost%20in%20the%20end%20after%20winning%20everything%20before%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20spiritual%20help%20is%20indicated%2C%20such%20as%20can%20come%20only%20if%20they%20first%20get%20used%20to%20wearing%20saffron%20uniforms%20at%20all%20practice%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20talisman%20works%20in%20politics%2C%20how%20can%20it%20not%20work%20in%20cricket%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20armed%2C%20no%20team%20from%20an%20erstwhile%20penal%20colony%20may%20ever%20have%20the%20gumption%20to%20best%20our%20hegemony%20of%20thousands%20of%20years%20over%20world%20history%2C%20even%20if%20there%20was%20no%20cricket%20in%20Vedic%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20matter%20of%20renaming%20the%20stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%20may%20also%20be%20entrusted%20to%20a%20high%20table%20of%20astrologers%20for%20corrective%20remedies%2C%20so%20that%20come%20a%20next%20final%20match%20in%20that%20hallowed%20arena%2C%20the%20stars%20may%20mandate%20our%20victory%20before%20the%20first%20ball%20is%20bowled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo