.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67445233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20International%20Energy%20Agency%20says%20the%20sector%20must%20choose%20between%20worsening%20the%20climate%20crisis%20or%20helping%20solve%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A56%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67445233%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67445233.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67445233.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%3A%20How%20the%20Political%20Discourse%20Around%20Census%20Has%20Changed%20in%20the%20Last%20Few%20Decades%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28173252%2FIMG_4426.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20obsession%20with%20population%20statistics%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(J%26amp%3BK)%20is%20as%20old%20as%20the%20contested%20accession%20of%20the%20state%20to%20India%20and%20the%20occupation%20of%20parts%20of%20it%20by%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20rekindled%2C%20most%20recently%2C%20in%202019%20by%20the%20repeal%20of%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20which%20stripped%20away%20provisions%20that%20offered%20autonomy%20to%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20population%20figures%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20data%20tends%20to%20be%20moot.%20The%20politics%20of%20numbers%20that%20shapes%20and%20is%20shaped%20by%20census%20statistics%20merits%20closer%20attention%20in%20this%20context%2C%20specifically%20its%20shifting%20nature%20between%201991%20and%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20erstwhile%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20the%20only%20state%20of%20India%20that%20missed%20the%20census%20twice%20after%201947%2C%20first%20in%201951%20and%20then%20again%20in%201991%2C%20due%20to%20political%20instability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%20and%202011%2C%20the%20census%20was%20conducted%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20but%20the%20exercise%20was%20impaired%20by%20the%20interference%20of%20partisans%20of%20independence%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20who%20feared%20that%20New%20Delhi%20wanted%20to%20manipulate%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20comprised%20three%20administrative%20divisions%20in%20India%3A%20Jammu%2C%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh.%20According%20to%20the%20census%2C%20Kashmiri-speaking%20Muslims%20constitute%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20division%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20state%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20communally%20motivated%20attacks%20amid%20an%20armed%20insurgency%20precipitated%20the%20exodus%20of%20almost%20the%20entire%20indigenous%20Hindu%20population%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindus%20constitute%20a%20majority%20in%20Jammu%3B%20in%20recent%20decades%2C%20Muslims%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20largest%20religious%20community%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashmiri-speaking%20Sunni%20Muslims%20and%20Dogri-speaking%20upper%20caste%20Hindus%2C%20the%20dominant%20communities%20of%20Kashmir%20and%20Jammu%2C%20respectively%2C%20have%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20zero-sum%20game%20over%20representation%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20and%20share%20in%20public%20spending%20and%20jobs%20since%20the%201950s%20(other%20communities%20such%20as%20Gujjars%2C%20Bakarwals%20and%20Paharis%20joined%20the%20contest%20over%20public%20resources%20in%20more%20recent%20decades).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjammu-kashmir-domicile-law-article-35a-permanent-resident%5C%22%3EThroughout%20History%2C%20Demographic%20Changes%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20Have%20Only%20Deepened%20Conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20these%20communities%20hold%20divergent%20preferences%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20political%20future%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20They%20have%20been%20concerned%20about%20the%20religious%20composition%20of%20the%20headcount%20because%20it%20is%20widely%20believed%20that%20the%20relative%20population%20shares%20of%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus%20would%20determine%20who%20controls%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20the%20unlikely%20scenario%20of%20a%20plebiscite%20over%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20affiliation%20to%20India%2C%20as%20recommended%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20(UNSC)%20back%20in%201948%20after%20India%20approached%20the%20body%20when%20tribal%20raiders%20backed%20by%20Pakistan%20invaded%20the%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20every%20political%20move%20and%20administrative%20policy%20is%20parsed%20for%20implications%20for%20the%20numerical%20dominance%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20which%20gives%20it%20%E2%80%93%20and%20by%20extension%20its%20Muslim-majority%20population%20%E2%80%93%20a%20larger%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20politics%20of%20numbers%20has%2C%20however%2C%20transformed%20over%20the%20past%20few%20decades%2C%20which%20can%20be%20explained%20by%20the%20tension%20between%20%3Ci%3Emardamshumari%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(census)%20and%C2%A0%3Ci%3Eraishumari%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(plebiscite)%20in%20the%20Valley.%20We%20will%20examine%20three%20iterations%20of%20this%20shifting%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%201991%20census%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20census%20was%20scheduled%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20in%201991%2C%20but%20was%20eventually%20cancelled%20barely%20a%20week%20before%20its%20start%20date%20because%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20field%20situation%E2%80%9D%20did%20not%20%E2%80%9Cpermit%E2%80%9D%20enumeration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20bears%20noting%20that%20in%201990-91%2C%20the%20insurgency%20was%20limited%20to%20the%20Valley%2C%20while%20Ladakh%20and%20most%20districts%20of%20Jammu%20were%20free%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.satp.org%2Fdatasheet-terrorist-attack%2Findia-jammukashmir%2FJ-and-K-Fatalities-1988-2000%5C%22%3Efatality%20rate%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20much%20less%20than%20that%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.satp.org%2Fdatasheet-terrorist-attack%2Findia-punjab%2Findia-punjab-fatalities-between-1981-2000%5C%22%3Eneighbouring%20Punjab%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20also%20grappling%20with%20an%20armed%20insurgency.%20The%20census%20and%20elections%20were%20held%20in%20Punjab%2C%20even%20as%20the%20entire%20state%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20kept%20out%20of%20both%20the%20exercises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20census%20operations%20were%20threatened%20by%20insurgents%20and%20the%20census%20office%20was%20burned%20down%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20census%20was%20specifically%20targeted%20as%20the%20whole%20range%20of%20state%20machinery%20came%20under%20attack%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fall-is-not-well-in-jammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%3EAll%20Is%20Not%20Well%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disarray%20within%20the%20general%20administration%20rather%20than%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20insurgency%20was%20the%20primary%20reason%20why%20the%20census%20was%20cancelled%20in%201991%20(the%20census%20was%20conducted%20in%202000-01%2C%20the%20most%20violent%20years%20of%20the%20insurgency).%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20armed%20insurgency%20disrupted%20elections%20and%20the%20census%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20and%20%E2%80%9Cembarrassed%E2%80%9D%20the%20Union%20government%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20country.%20So%2C%20in%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20New%20Delhi%20was%20determined%20to%20resume%20the%20census%20and%20generate%20a%20collective%20self-portrait%20of%20the%20country%20that%20included%20Muslim-majority%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResuming%20exercises%20such%20as%20the%20census%20and%20elections%20were%20seen%20as%20essential%20for%20restoring%20India%E2%80%99s%20self-image%20as%20a%20secular%20modern%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20by%20then%20the%20insurgency%20and%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20counterinsurgency%20had%20not%20only%20undermined%20the%20general%20administration%20that%20provides%20public%20goods%20(including%20statistics)%20but%20also%20deepened%20regional%20and%20communal%20polarisation%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20build%20consensus%20on%20the%20provision%20of%20public%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20insistence%20on%20conducting%20a%20census%20under%20these%20circumstances%20meant%20that%20the%20availability%20of%20statistics%20enjoyed%20a%20priority%20over%20quality.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%202001%20census%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3EThis%20is%20the%20larger%20context%20within%20which%20insurgent%20and%20armed%20militant%20organisations%20such%20as%20the%20Hizbul%20Mujahideen%20(HM)%2C%20among%20others%2C%20called%20for%20a%20boycott%20of%20the%20census%20in%202000%20and%20warned%20officials%20against%20participating%20in%20the%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20one%20government%20employees%E2%80%99%20union%20leader%20asked%20its%20members%20to%20skip%20census%20duties%20until%20there%20was%20clarity%20on%20their%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20October%201%2C%202000%20was%20the%20reference%20date%20for%20the%202001%20census%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20However%2C%20this%20reference%20date%20was%20postponed%20in%20a%20haphazard%20and%20piecemeal%20manner%20across%20districts%20due%20to%20the%20boycott%20call%20that%20severely%20disrupted%20the%20census%20throughout%20the%20Valley%20and%20Doda%20district%20of%20Jammu.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnew-special-status-thrust-on-jk-is-an-abuse-of-the-constitution-and-a-danger-to-the-republic%5C%22%3ENew%20Special%20Status%20Thrust%20on%20J%26amp%3BK%20Is%20an%20Abuse%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20a%20Danger%20to%20the%20Republic%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContemporary%20commentary%20catalogued%20the%20boycott%20as%20another%20fallout%20of%20the%20secessionist%20insurgency.%20The%20HM%E2%80%99s%20boycott%20call%20can%2C%20however%2C%20be%20read%20through%20several%20different%20lenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20it%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20refusal%20to%20acquiesce%20in%20activities%20that%20normalise%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20claim%20to%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20it%20reflects%20communal%20anxiety%20in%20the%20Valley%20about%20demographic%20change%20that%20could%20erode%20the%20Muslim%20majority%20character%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20While%20these%20longstanding%20macro-concerns%20can%20account%20for%20the%20rationale%20of%20the%20boycott%2C%20they%20leave%20factors%20that%20precipitated%20and%20enforced%20the%20boycott%20unexplained.%20This%20is%20where%20a%20third%20lens%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompetition%20among%20pro-independence%20groups%20and%20political%20parties%20under%20the%20shadow%20of%20a%20nascent%20engagement%20between%20pro-independence%20groups%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20can%20help%20better%20understand%20the%20politicisation%20of%20the%202001%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possibility%20of%20direct%20engagement%20between%20a%20section%20of%20the%20HM%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20alarmed%20the%20Hurriyat%20Conference%2C%20an%20overground%20alliance%20of%20political%20and%20religious%20organisations%20campaigning%20for%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20separation%20from%20India%2C%20that%20claimed%20to%20be%20the%20true%20representative%20of%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sharp%20exchange%20ensued%20between%20the%20HM%20and%20the%20Hurriyat.%20The%20HM%20advised%20the%20Hurriyat%20to%20focus%20on%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2F2000%2F20000909%2Fj%26amp%3Bk.htm%232%5C%22%3Ethe%20conspiracies%20being%20hatched%20against%20the%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20rather%20than%20attack%20the%20ceasefire%20initiative.%20The%20possible%20use%20of%20the%20census%20to%20alter%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20demography%20was%20one%20of%20the%20conspiracies%20that%20the%20HM%20highlighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20two%20sides%20patched%20up%20soon%2C%20the%20politicisation%20and%20communalisation%20of%20the%20census%20proved%20irreversible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-review-kashmir-shia-sunni-hakim-sameer-hamdani%5C%22%3EKashmir%E2%80%99s%201.5%20Million%20Shiites%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Fit%20Into%20a%20Single%20Mould%20%E2%80%93%20Neither%20Can%20Their%20History%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20the%20ruling%20National%20Conference%20was%20dealing%20with%20anti-incumbency%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202002%20assembly%20elections.%20It%20was%20struggling%20to%20protect%20its%20political%20turf%20amid%20twin%20pressures%20generated%20by%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Fifth%20Pay%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%2C%20which%20worsened%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20finances%20and%20limited%20the%20fiscal%20space%20for%20developmental%20initiatives%2C%20and%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20outreach%20to%20pro-independence%20groups%20and%20rejection%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20partisan%20autonomy%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaif-ud-Din%20Soz%20%E2%80%93%20a%20politician%20who%20had%20been%20expelled%20from%20the%20NC%20a%20few%20years%20earlier%20for%20defying%20a%20whip%20%E2%80%93%20chose%20to%20question%20the%20impartiality%20of%20the%20census%20to%20present%20himself%20as%20the%20authentic%20voice%20of%20Kashmir.%20Soz%20issued%20two%20press%20statements%20after%20the%20HM%E2%80%99s%20boycott%20call%20to%20elaborate%20the%20alleged%20threat%20of%20demographic%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20amid%20the%20political%20uncertainty%20generated%20by%20the%20nascent%20peace%20process%2C%20a%20variety%20of%20actors%20within%20the%20mainstream%20political%20parties%20and%20the%20pro-independence%20camp%20tried%20to%20secure%20their%20support%20base%20by%20tapping%20into%20communal%20passions%20inflamed%20by%20the%20alleged%20threat%20to%20the%20demographic%20composition%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%202011%20census%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20long%20run-up%20to%20the%202011%20census%20was%20dotted%20with%20demographic%20controversies%20reminiscent%20of%20the%201980s%20and%201990s.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20the%20pro-independence%20groups%20called%20for%20participation%20in%20the%20census%20(and%20also%2C%20elections)%20to%20stall%20attempts%20to%20undermine%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20demographic%20dominance%20and%20share%20in%20the%20state%20legislature%20and%20development%20funding.%20This%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20sudden%20development.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20even%20during%20the%202001%20census%2C%20certain%20communities%20within%20Kashmir%20were%20supportive%20of%20the%20exercise.%20Gujjar%20and%20Bakarwal%20tribes%2C%20which%20comprise%20the%20third%20largest%20population%20group%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20have%20a%20significant%20presence%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FCensus_of_India_2001%2F_IuHzzQyyG0C%5C%22%3Eevinced%20an%20extraordinary%20interest%20in%20their%20enumeration%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20because%20they%20viewed%20the%20census%20as%20essential%20to%20engage%20the%20developmental%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%2C%20however%2C%20demanded%20steps%20to%20address%20concerns%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20about%20the%20undercount%20of%20the%20nomadic%20part%20of%20the%20community%20under%20the%C2%A0%3Ci%3Ede%20facto%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0method%20(in%20which%20individuals%20are%20counted%20where%20they%20are%20normally%20residents%20during%20the%20period%20of%20enumeration).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Why%20the%20Delimitation%20Exercise%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Calls%20for%20Caution%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-delimitation-exercise-caution-census-population-data%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20Delimitation%20Exercise%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Calls%20for%20Caution%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20even%20the%20HM%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20on%20the%202001%20census%20were%20framed%20in%C2%A0%3Ci%3Estatistical%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(concerns%20about%20the%20undercount%20of%20migrants%20under%20the%C2%A0%3Ci%3Ede%20facto%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0method)%20and%C2%A0%3Ci%3Edevelopmental%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(fear%20of%20obstruction%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2F2000%2F20000909%2Fj%26amp%3Bk.htm%232%5C%22%3Eavenues%20of%20development%20for%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20if%20Kashmir%20loses%20the%20majority)%20terms%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20its%20older%20and%20broader%20concerns%20about%20the%20Indian%20state%E2%80%99s%20legitimacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20there%20was%20a%20more%20general%20shift%20from%20violent%20opposition%20to%20the%20census%20to%20its%20manipulation%20to%20secure%20a%20larger%20share%20of%20the%20public%20pie%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20politically%20restive%20ethno-geographic%20periphery.%20This%20was%20seen%20in%202001%20in%20states%20such%20as%20Nagaland%20and%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20across%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fbooks%2Fnumbers-in-indias-periphery%2FFE6168238548B42FE99CC6C7896CACE3%5C%22%3Eperiphery%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0can%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20twin%20developments%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20nationalist%20insurgencies%20degenerated%20into%20sub-nationalist%20conflicts%20over%20redistribution.%20On%20the%20other%2C%20the%20retreat%20of%20the%20state%20after%20the%20liberalisation%20of%20the%20economy%20added%20urgency%20to%20capture%20public%20resources%20in%20the%20economically%20stagnant%20periphery%20where%20trust%20in%20the%20impartiality%20of%20public%20institutions%20is%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Edata%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0deficit%20of%20the%20periphery%20is%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fbooks%2Fabs%2Fnumbers-in-indias-periphery%2Fdata-development-and-democracy%2F5661A78C10E4CF0BE1437ABD7306C845%5C%22%3Eintertwined%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20its%C2%A0%3Cem%3Edemocracy%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Cem%3Edevelopment%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0deficits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shifting%20politics%20around%20the%20census%20during%201991-2011%20can%2C%20therefore%2C%20be%20accounted%20for%20by%20the%20competition%20between%20mainstream%20political%20actors%20and%20pro-independence%20groups%20that%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20unfolded%20within%20the%20larger%20political-economic%20context%20defined%20by%20the%20liberalisation%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%20that%20reshaped%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20these%20non-demographic%20developments%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20census%20statistics%20and%20public%20policy%20is%20a%20story%20for%20another%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EVikas%20Kumar%20teaches%20economics%20at%20Azim%20Premji%20University%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20is%20the%20author%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fbooks%2Fnumbers-as-political-allies%2F4FB6F90A77F38501629062AA2DD4DA1C%5C%22%3ENumbers%20as%20Political%20Allies%3A%20The%20Census%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0(Cambridge%20University%20Press%2C%202023).%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20originally%20appeared%20in%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fcasi.sas.upenn.edu%2Fiit%5C%22%3EIndia%20in%20Transition%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20publication%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%E2%80%99s%20Center%20for%20the%20Advanced%20Study%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700710244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28173252%2FIMG_4426.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-politics-of-numbers-in-kashmir-plebiscite-to-census%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20transformation%20of%20Kashmir's%20politics%20of%20numbers%20over%20the%20last%20few%20decades%20can%20be%20explained%20by%20the%20tension%20between%20%E2%80%98mardamshumari%E2%80%99%C2%A0(census)%20and%C2%A0%E2%80%98raishumari%E2%80%99%C2%A0(plebiscite).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-politics-of-numbers-in-kashmir-plebiscite-to-census%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rainbow%20Bridge%3A%20US-Canada%20border%20blast%20not%20terror-related%2C%20says%20NY%20governor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700710235000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F121B9%2Fproduction%2F_131796147_explosion.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67502406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20husband%20and%20wife%20died%20in%20a%20fireball%20as%20their%20vehicle%20hurtled%20into%20a%20checkpoint%20at%20Rainbow%20Bridge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1753%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67502406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67502406.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67502406.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20G20%20Virtual%20Summit%2C%20PM%20Modi%20Highlights%20%E2%80%98Convergence%E2%80%99%20Over%20West%20Asia%20Conflict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23085246%2FF_jJLdsbcAAxKE3.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20that%20there%20was%20a%20seven-point%20%E2%80%9Cconvergence%E2%80%9D%20among%20G-20%20leaders%20about%20the%20Hamas-Israel%20war%2C%20including%20the%20need%20for%20a%20two-state%20solution%2C%20even%20as%20he%20hoped%20that%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20will%20not%20escalate%20into%20a%20regional%20conflagration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20Ukraine%20was%20also%20discussed%2C%20with%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20urging%20measures%20to%20halt%20the%20unfolding%20%E2%80%9Ctragedy%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20observers%20claimed%20was%20his%20most%20conciliatory%20remarks%20in%20recent%20times%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20chaired%20the%20last%20G20%20meeting%20of%20the%20year-long%20rotating%20Indian%20presidency%2C%20joining%20leaders%20across%20the%20globe%20in%20a%20virtual%20conference.%20India%20will%20be%20handing%20over%20the%20presidency%20to%20Brazil%20on%20December%201.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20major%20leaders%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20did%20not%20participate.%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20who%20had%20also%20not%20travelled%20to%20India%20for%20the%20summit%2C%20was%20also%20missing.%20However%2C%20another%20notable%20absentee%20at%20the%20Delhi%20summit%2C%20Putin%2C%20took%20part%20in%20the%20virtual%20conference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Death%20of%20civilians%20condemnable%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1978867%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eopening%20remarks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20new%20challenges%20have%20arisen%20since%20the%20Delhi%20summit%20in%20September.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20of%20insecurity%20and%20instability%20in%20the%20West%20Asia%20region%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20for%20all%20of%20us.%C2%A0Our%20coming%20together%20today%20symbolizes%20that%20we%20are%20sensitive%20to%20all%20issues%20and%20stand%20together%20to%20resolve%20them.%20We%20believe%20that%20terrorism%20is%20unacceptable%20to%20all%20of%20us.%20The%20death%20of%20civilians%2C%20wherever%20they%20happen%2C%20is%20condemnable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%207%2C%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20terror%20attack%20from%20Gaza%20into%20Israel%2C%20killing%20over%201%2C400%20people%20and%20taking%20scores%20of%20hostages.%20In%20retaliation%2C%20Israel%20launched%20air%20strikes%2C%20followed%20by%20ground%20operations%20inside%20Gaza%20which%20has%20killed%20over%2013%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20six%20weeks%20of%20continuous%20violence%2C%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20Hamas%20announced%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20on%20November%2022%2C%20that%20they%20have%20reached%20a%20deal%20for%20the%20release%20of%2050%20hostages%20for%20150%20Palestinian%20prisoners%2C%20along%20with%20a%20humanitarian%20%E2%80%98pause%E2%80%99%20for%20at%20least%20four%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWelcoming%20the%20news%20about%20the%20hostage%20deal%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20he%20hoped%20that%20all%20hostages%20were%20released%20and%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Ctimely%20and%20continuous%20delivery%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20does%20not%20take%20any%20regional%20form%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1978953%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20conclusion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20virtual%20summit%20which%20lasted%20over%20three%20hours%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20after%20hearing%20all%20the%20leaders%2C%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cconvergence%E2%80%9D%20(s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eahmati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20on%20many%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20conflict%20in%20West%20Asia%20at%20the%20G20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20listed%20seven%20points%20on%20which%20there%20was%20commonality%20of%20views%2C%20ranging%20from%20zero%20tolerance%20of%20terrorism%20to%20declaring%20that%20the%20deaths%20of%20%E2%80%9Cinnocent%20people%E2%80%9D%2C%20especially%20women%20and%20children%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20acceptable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20diplomacy%20and%20dialogue%20was%20the%20only%20way%2C%20Modi%20also%20cited%20a%20permanent%20%E2%80%98two-state%20solution%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20dispute%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cconvergence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20G20%20is%20ready%20to%20provide%20all%20support%20in%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98No%20G20%20proposal%20on%20West%20Asia%20as%20such%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWas%20there%20a%20G20%20proposal%20(on%20West%20Asia)%20as%20such%3F%20No%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%20that%20there%20was%20universal%20welcome%20for%20Wednesday%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20of%20a%20hostage%20release%20deal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20answer%20to%20another%20query%20at%20the%20media%20briefing%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20while%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20leaders%20had%20batted%20for%20the%20two-state%20solution%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20there%20was%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20two-state%20solution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20whole%20idea%20spillover%E2%80%A6honestly%2C%20I%20would%20say%20the%20focus%20is%20right%20now%20on%20ensuring%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20spill%20over%20to%20beyond%20where%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Military%20operations%20are%20always%20a%20tragedy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20West%20Asia%2C%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20also%20figured%2C%20especially%20with%20Russian%20President%20Putin%20addressing%20the%20G20%20meeting%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20invasion%20in%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20our%20colleagues%20here%20have%20mentioned%20that%20they%20are%20shocked%20by%20%E2%80%98Russia%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20aggression%20in%20Ukraine.%E2%80%99%20Indeed%2C%20military%20operations%20are%20always%20a%20tragedy%20for%20specific%20people%2C%20specific%20families%2C%20and%20the%20country%20as%20a%20whole.%20And%20we%20must%20certainly%20think%20about%20how%20to%20stop%20this%20tragedy%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fen.kremlin.ru%2Fevents%2Fpresident%2Fnews%2F72790%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20remarked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20asserted%20that%20Russia%20%E2%80%9Chas%20never%20refused%20to%20negotiate%20peace%20with%20Ukraine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20Russia%2C%20but%20Ukraine%20that%20has%20publicly%20announced%20that%20it%20is%20withdrawing%20from%20the%20negotiation%20process.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20leader%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20prohibiting%20such%20negotiations%20with%20Russia%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20Putin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fputin-we-must-think-how-stop-the-tragedy-ukraine-2023-11-22%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EReuters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20remarks%20at%20the%20G-20%20virtual%20meeting%20were%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20Putin%E2%80%99s%20most%20dovish%20on%20the%20war%20for%20months%20and%20contrasts%20with%20his%20sometimes%20long%20diatribes%20about%20the%20failings%20and%20arrogance%20of%20the%20United%20States%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700710226000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23085246%2FF_jJLdsbcAAxKE3.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg20-virtual-summit-modi-israel-palestine-two-state-jaishankar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stating%20that%20diplomacy%20and%20dialogue%20was%20the%20only%20way%2C%20Modi%20also%20cited%20a%20permanent%20'two-state%20solution'%20to%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20dispute%20as%20part%20of%20the%20'consensus.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg20-virtual-summit-modi-israel-palestine-two-state-jaishankar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Class%20IV%20student%20made%20to%20do%20sit-ups%20in%20Odisha%2C%20dies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700709728000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105431436%2Cimgsize-13910.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbhubaneswar%2Fclass-iv-student-dies-odisha-school%2Farticleshow%2F105430884.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http