3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20a%20joint%20team%20of%20security%20forces%20comprising%20the%20Army%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20among%20other%20central%20paramilitary%20forces%20launched%20a%20search%20operation%20in%20a%20forested%20area%20of%20Gulabgarh%20in%20Kalakote%20tehsil%20of%20Rajouri%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20mopping%20operation%20entered%20its%20fourth%20day%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20the%20joint%20team%20came%20under%20intense%20fire%20by%20a%20group%20of%20two%20to%20three%20heavily%20armed%20militants%20in%20Baajimal%20area.%20Sources%20said%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20fire%20was%20so%20high%20that%20the%20joint%20team%20had%20to%20retreat%2C%20leaving%20some%20of%20the%20injured%20behind%2C%20and%20regroup%2C%20before%20taking%20on%20the%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Peoples%20Anti-Fascist%20Force%20(PAFF)%20which%20the%20officials%20believe%20is%20an%20offshoot%20of%20the%20banned%2C%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20outfit%2C%20Jaish-e-Mohammad%2C%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack%2C%20according%20to%20open%20source%20intelligence%20posts%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0couldn%E2%80%99t%20immediately%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20these%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deadly%20shootout%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fkokernag-operation-anantnag-fourth-soldier-killed%5C%22%3Ebears%20resemblance%20to%20a%20similar%20attack%20on%20security%20forces%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kokernag%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20in%20which%20the%20Army%20lost%20a%20Commanding%20Officer%20and%20a%20Major%20among%20four%20soldiers%20while%20an%20injured%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20awaiting%20rescue%2C%20bled%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Kokernag%20operation%2C%20security%20forces%20were%20following%20a%20tip-off%20about%20the%20presence%20of%20militants%20in%20the%20mountainous%20Gadool%20village%20which%20led%20them%20into%20an%20ambush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-risk%20operation%2C%20in%20which%20militants%20are%20known%20to%20leverage%20the%20heights%20of%20mountains%20and%20dense%20vegetation%20to%20their%20strategic%20advantage%2C%20turned%20into%20one%20of%20the%20deadliest%20attacks%20on%20security%20forces%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strategic%20advantages%20of%20height%20and%20thick%20forest%20cover%20had%20stretched%20the%20encounter%20in%20Gadool%20to%20six%20days%20as%20security%20forces%20proceeded%20cautiously%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20more%20casualties%20in%20their%20ranks%20while%20closing%20in%20around%20the%20perpetrators%20who%20were%20hiding%20on%20a%20mountainside%20with%20natural%2C%20cave-like%20structures%20beneath%20a%20canopy%20of%20dense%20vegetation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20PAFF%20militants%20deliberately%20showed%20up%20in%20residential%20areas%20of%20Rajouri%20recently%20to%20bait%20the%20security%20forces%20and%20draw%20them%20out%20on%20a%20manhunt%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20the%20hilly%20district%20without%20assessing%20the%20risks%20remains%20a%20matter%20of%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20shot%20near%20the%20site%20of%20the%20shootout%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20shows%20two%20men%20in%20civvies%20accompanying%20a%20team%20of%20Army%20soldiers%20who%20are%20hauling%20a%20cot%20down%20a%20hillock%20on%20their%20shoulders.%20An%20unidentified%20body%2C%20purportedly%20one%20of%20the%20Army%20soldiers%20killed%20in%20the%20shootout%2C%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20video%20laying%20motionless%20on%20the%20cot%20under%20a%20red%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20immediately%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20slain%20soldiers%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Captain%20MV%20Pranjal%2