20tighter%20financial%20conditions%20throughout%20the%20economy.%20Strong%20spending%20was%20responsible%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthank-the-american-retail-consumer-for-the-soft-landing-2023-7%5C%22%3Ebuoying%20economic%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgdp-recession-outlook-economy-gross-domestic-product-third-quarter-2023-10%5C%22%3EGDP%20growing%20at%20a%20breakneck%20pace%20of%204.9%25%20over%20the%20third%20quarter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20signs%20that%20consumer%20strength%20is%20deteriorating%2C%20and%20the%20great%20American%20spending%20spree%20could%20be%20grinding%20to%20a%20halt%2C%20according%20to%20Deloitte%20chief%20economist%20Ira%20Kalish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20consumer%20slowdown%20has%20begun%2C%26quot%3B%20Kalish%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.deloitte.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Finsights%2Feconomy%2Fglobal-economic-outlook%2Fweekly-update.html%3Ficid%3Dinsights_top_weekly-update%5C%22%3Enote%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BThe%20stellar%20US%20economic%20growth%20recorded%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20was%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20strong%20growth%20in%20consumer%20spending.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20widely%20expected%20that%20consumer%20spending%20will%20decelerate%20in%20the%20holiday%20season%2C%20thereby%20putting%20financial%20stress%20on%20retailers%20and%20their%20suppliers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20consumer%20slowdown%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20the%20economy%20is%20about%20to%20slip%20into%20a%20recession%2C%20but%20it%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomy-consumer-spending-credit-card-debt-delinquencies-retail-hiring-2023-11%5C%22%3Epush%20the%20economy%20closer%20to%20a%20downturn%20as%20a%20pillar%20of%20strength%20is%20taken%20out.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%2