20lover%20and%20live%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20for%20you%20to%20never%20have%20heard%20about%20the%20Chik%20community.%20Such%20is%20the%20nature%20of%20their%20occupation.%20Things%20may%20have%20changed%20a%20bit%20now%2C%20but%20earlier%20both%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus%20used%20to%20purchase%20mutton%20from%20them.%20The%20community%20never%20discriminated%20against%20anyone%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20believe%20that%20the%20Chik%20community%20is%20the%20same%20as%20the%20Kasai%20or%20Kasab%20community.%20But%20they%20are%20two%20different%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Chik%20people%20trade%20in%20the%20meat%20of%20small%20animals%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Qureshi%20community%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Kasai%2C%20trade%20in%20the%20meat%20of%20big%20animals.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20difference%20between%20the%20status%20and%20population%20of%20both%20these%20castes.%20While%20the%20population%20of%20the%20Kasab%20community%20is%201%2C33%2C807%2C%20that%20of%20the%20Chik%20community%20is%20almost%20half%2C%20at%2050%2C404.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20361px)%2085vw%2C%20361px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22361%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22517%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20status%2C%20both%20Chik%20and%20Kasab%2FKasai%20are%20considered%20Arzal%20(equivalent%20to%20Dalits).%20Most%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Chik%20caste%20are%20very%20poor%20and%20their%20condition%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Hindu%20Dalit%20Khatik%20caste.%20The%20traditional%20occupation%20of%20the%20Khatik%20caste%20is%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20the%20Chik%20caste.%20The%20only%20difference%20is%20that%20Muslims%20consider%20the%20meat%20slaughtered%20by%20Chik%20people%20halal%20(allowed%20for%20consumption)%20while%20it%20is%20considered%20forbidden%20for%20Hindus.%20Similarly%2C%20Hindus%20are%20allowed%20to%20eat%20meat%20slaughtered%20by%20a%20Khatik%20while%20Muslims%20consider%20it%20haram%20(prohibited).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chik%20community%20is%20also%20addressed%20by%20many%20other%20names%20such%20as%20Bakar%20Kasab%20or%20Buj%20Kasab.%20Bakar%20means%20goat.%20At%20some%20places%20people%20call%20them%20Chikwa.%20This%20form%20of%20address%2C%20with%20an%20added%20syllable%2C%20is%20quite%20common%20in%20Bihar.%20For%20instance%2C%20Gowala%20becomes%20Gowarva%2C%20Dhobi%20become%20Dhobiya%2C%20Chamar%20becomes%20Chamra.%20It%20is%20usually%20done%20with%20a%20derogatory%20purpose.%20Many%20a%20times%2C%20the%20upper%20castes%20are%20also%20referred%20people%20in%20such%20a%20way.%20For%20instance%2C%20Pandit%20becomes%20Panditwa%2C%20Bhumihar%20becomes%20Bhumiharwa%2C%20and%20Rajput%20becomes%20Rajputwa.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20upper%20castes%20this%20change%20happened%20after%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20salutations%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20considered%20a%20culturally%20rich%20state.%20Here%2C%20people%20address%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Chik%20caste%20as%20Bakar%20Kasab%20or%20Buj%20Kasab.%20Most%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Chik%20community%20live%20in%20these%20two%20states.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20they%20mainly%20inhabit%20the%20areas%20of%20Rohilkhand%20and%20Awadh.%20Bareilly%2C%20Bijnor%2C%20Badaun%20and%20Shahjahanpur%20districts%20of%20Rohilkhand%20have%20a%20significant%20population%20of%20the%20caste.%20In%20Awadh%2C%20the%20population%20is%20mainly%20found%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20Kheri%2C%20Unnao%20and%20Hardoi%20districts.%20However%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Chik%20caste%20are%20spread%20over%20almost%20every%20district%20of%20Bihar.%20Apart%20from%20India%2C%20the%20community%20also%20lives%20in%20Karachi%20and%20Lahore%20in%20Pakistan.%20No%20matter%20where%20they%20live%2C%20India%20or%20Pakistan%2C%20their%20job%20is%20the%20same%20%E2%80%93%20slaughtering%20goats%20and%20trading%20in%20its%20meat%20and%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sachar%20Committee%20mentioned%20the%20Chik%20community%20in%20its%20report%20as%20well%2C%20but%20the%20real%20question%20is%20about%20the%20implementation%20of%20its%20recommendations.%20In%20both%20Bihar%20and%20UP%2C%20this%20caste%20is%20included%20in%20the%20backward%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20their%20political%20status%20is%20concerned%2C%20their%20participation%20is%20absolutely%20negligible.%20For%20social%20status%20in%20India%2C%20numbers%20are%20important%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20why%20a%20minuscule%20population%20of%20only%2050%2C000%20means%20they%20are%20deprived%20of%20almost%20every%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20controversy%20around%20jhatka%20and%20halal%20meat%2C%20their%20livelihood%20is%20under%20attack.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20Chik%20people%20have%20now%20started%20entering%20other%20occupations%20and%20are%20leaving%20their%20traditional%20profession.%20But%20no%20change%20happens%20overnight.%20It%20will%20take%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260838%2Fbihar-caste-survey-how-chik-caste-is-different-from-qureshis%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-nai-hajjaam%5C%22%3ENai%2FHajjaam%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-pasi%5C%22%3EPasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-rangrez%5C%22%3ERangrez%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chamar%5C%22%3EChamar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-gorkan%5C%22%3EGorkan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-jutt%5C%22%3EJutt%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-yadav%5C%22%3EYadav%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20series%20is%20available%20in%20Hindi%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2Fauthor%2Fnaval-kishor-kumar%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%