ool%20and%20the%2019%20students%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20village%20sits%20near%20the%20border%2C%20and%20with%20poor%20roads%2C%20commuting%20to%20schools%20outside%20daily%20isn%E2%80%99t%20feasible.%20If%20this%20school%20closes%2C%20it%E2%80%99ll%20disrupt%20many%20farmers%E2%80%99%20lives.%20They%20might%20need%20to%20move%20to%20Assam%2C%20straining%20resources%20and%20losing%20their%20income.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20them%20to%20worry%20about%20where%20their%20kids%20go%20to%20school.%20We%20only%20want%20them%20to%20focus%20on%20their%20farms%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nambie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20school%20has%20increased%20from%2019%20to%2085.%20They%20do%20this%20for%20free%2C%20only%20charging%20a%20nominal%20fee%20to%20pay%20the%20other%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20spare%20time%2C%20the%20couple%20tends%20to%20a%20farm%2C%20cultivating%20lemongrass.%20They%20sell%20lemongrass%20oil%2C%20while%20Nambie%20pursues%20her%20passion%20for%20pickling%20by%20starting%20a%20pickle%20business.%20She%20also%20dreams%20of%20opening%20a%20restaurant%20someday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%20important%20to%20Nambie%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332322%2Fabha-singhaal-khichdi-express-model-cloud-kitchen-entreprenuer-business-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20or%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20connected%20to%20food%20and%20I%20really%20enjoy%20being%20around%20children.%20You%20learn%20something%20new%20in%20both%20teaching%20and%20cooking.%20Every%20day%20is%20a%20new%20day%20in%20the%20kitchen%20as%20well%20as%20the%20classroom.%20I%20love%20it.%20Why%20would%20I%20choose%20between%20the%20two%3F%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Nambie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E