%3ELPG%20cylinders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20counter%20the%20Congress%20on%20cheaper%20LPG%20cylinders%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%20to%20provide%20them%20at%20Rs%20450%20to%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20in%20its%20manifesto%20has%20said%20that%20while%20the%20state%20government%20at%20present%20provides%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20500%20they%20will%20decrease%20it%20further%20to%20Rs%20400%20if%20voted%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20it%20will%20extend%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20country%E2%80%99s%20most%20affordable%20LPG%20cylinder%20scheme%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%20500%2C%20to%20families%20under%20the%20NFSA%20(National%20Food%20Security%20Act)%20and%20BPL%20(Below%20Poverty%20Line)%20categories%E2%80%9D%20and%20commit%20to%20further%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20gas%20cylinders%20to%20Rs%20400%20for%20Ujjwala%2C%20NFSA%2C%20and%20BPL%20families%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouth%20and%20employment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%2010%20lakh%20employment%20opportunities%20including%204%20lakh%20in%20the%20government%20sector%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%20to%20provide%202.5%20lakh%20government%20jobs%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20promised%20a%20new%20scheme%20for%20the%20recruitment%20of%20youngsters%20at%20the%20panchayat%20level%2C%20gradually%20merging%20with%20government%20vacancies.%20It%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20start%20a%20toll-free%20call%20centre%20and%20an%20e-Employment%20Exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-556745%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUnemployed%20youth%20protesting%20against%20irregularities%20which%20took%20place%20in%20government%20exams%20under%20Rajasthan%20Ekikrat%20Berozgaar%20Mahasangh.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FUpen%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%202.5%20lakh%20jobs%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20youth%20it%20has%20promised%20to%20set%20up%20a%20Rajasthan%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20Rajasthan%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%93%20modelled%20on%20AIIMS%20and%20IITs%20%E2%80%93%20in%20each%20division%2C%20among%20several%20other%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20rural%20jobs%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20increase%20employment%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20to%20150%20days%20of%20guaranteed%20work%20from%20125%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEducation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%20free%20English%20medium%20education%20to%20girls%20and%20boys%20and%20to%20bring%20an%20education%20guarantee%20law%20in%20the%20state%20and%20provide%20free%20education%20till%20class%2012%20as%20opposed%20to%20class%208%20under%20RTE%20(Right%20to%20Education).%20It%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20provide%20first-year%20students%20of%20government%20colleges%20with%20a%20free%20laptop%2Ftablet%20upon%20admission%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20promised%20free%20education%20from%20KG%20to%20PG%20to%20poor%20families%20and%20annual%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2012%2C000%20for%20students%20of%20poor%20families%20to%20purchase%20school%20bags%2C%20books%20and%20uniforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20Free%20Scooty%20Scheme%2C%20arrangements%20will%20be%20made%20to%20give%20free%20scooty%20to%20meritorious%20girl%20students%20after%20passing%20class%2012th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20government%20already%20operates%20a%20scheme%20in%20the%20state%20to%20provide%20scooters%20to%20students%20under%20the%20Kalibai%20Bhil%20Medhavi%20Chhatra%20Scooty%20Yojana%20to%20meritorious%20girl%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20double%20the%20coverage%20under%20its%20flagship%20health%20insurance%20scheme-the%20Mukhyamantri%20Nishulk%20Chiranjeevi%20Swasthya%20Bima%20Yojana%20from%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20scheme%20it%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20increase%20the%20facilities%20under%20free%20OPD%2FIPD%20in%20government%20medical%20institutions%20at%20the%20district%20and%20block%20level%20and%20include%20IVF%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20recognise%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20profound%20emotional%20and%20social%20challenges%20faced%20by%20couples%20deprived%20of%20the%20joy%20of%20parenthood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20has%20promised%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%20through%20the%20Bhamashah%20Health%20Infrastructure%20Mission%20and%20appointment%20of%2015%2C000%20doctors%20and%2020%2C000%20paramedical%20staff.%20It%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20set%20up%20350%20Jan%20Aushadi%20Kendras%20and%20at%20least%20one%20medical%20college%20in%20each%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20census%2C%20hate%20speech%20and%20Anti-Bharat%20cells%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%20to%20%E2%80%9Cto%20accurately%20determine%20population%20and%20allocate%20benefits%20for%20informed%20decisions%20on%20affirmative%20action.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20stringent%20measures%20against%20hate%20speech.%20The%20party%20has%20promised%20to%20%E2%80%9Cimplement%20and%20enforce%20stringent%20legal%20measures%20to%20address%20and%20penalise%20individuals%20engaged%20in%20hate%20speech.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20has%20promised%20to%20set%20up%20anti-Bharat%20sleeper%20cells%20and%20special%20police%20cells%20to%20tackle%20such%20cells%20along%20with%20establishing%20an%20anti-Gangster%20task%20force%20to%20stop%20gang%20wars%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20promises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20promised%20a%20law%20to%20implement%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%20and%20amending%20the%20Gig%20Workers%20Welfare%20Act%20to%20include%20auto%20and%20taxi%20drivers.%20In%20addition%C2%A0%20an%20Accountability%20and%20Auto%20Service%20Delivery%20Act%20has%20also%20been%20announced%20for%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20governance%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20announced%20the%20Vyapari%20Credit%20Card%20Scheme%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20Kisan%20Credit%20Card%20Scheme%2C%20to%20provide%20interest-free%20loans%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20small%20traders%2C%20shopkeepers%20and%20young%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20promised%20to%20set%20up%20the%20Rajasthan%20Economic%20Revival%20Task%20Force%20for%20the%20revival%20of%20the%20state%20economy%20and%20make%20Jaipur%2C%20Udaipur%2C%20Kota%2C%20Ajmer%2C%20Bharatpur%2C%20Jodhpur%20and%20Bikaner%20smart%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700658049000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22172044%2FThe-Wire-85.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffarmers-women-corruption-and-jobs-comparing-congress-bjps-rajasthan-manifestos%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20BJP%20has%20made%20alleged%20corruption%20in%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%2C%20alleged%20lack%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%20and%20paper%20leaks%20major%20poll%20issues%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20trying%20to%20buck%20the%20trend%20of%20revolving%20door%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20and%20make%20a%20comeback%20riding%20on%20its%20flagship%20schemes%20for%20social%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffarmers-women-corruption-and-jobs-comparing-congress-bjps-rajasthan-manifestos%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Unravelled%20Plot%20to%20Kill%20Khalistani%20Separatist%2C%20Lodged%20Protest%20With%20India%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22215159%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-22-at-9.45.19-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20United%20States%20warned%20Indian%20authorities%20about%20suspicion%20about%20their%20involvement%20in%20a%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20a%20Khalistani%20separatist%20on%20its%20soil%20and%20the%20plan%20was%20ultimately%20foiled%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20referring%20to%20a%20US%20protest%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%20issued%20a%20statement%20hours%20after%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20report%20admitting%20that%20Washington%20%E2%80%9Cshared%20some%20inputs%20pertaining%20to%20nexus%20between%20organised%20criminals%2C%20gun%20runners%2C%20terrorists%20and%20others%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20was%20being%20investigated%20by%20Indian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F56f7d6d6-6a93-4172-a49e-d8a91991e29d%5C%22%3EThe%20UK%20newspaper%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20target%20was%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20who%20is%20%E2%80%98general%20counsel%E2%80%99%20for%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%2C%20a%20US-based%20group%20that%20has%20been%20proscribed%20as%20a%20terror%20organisation%20by%20India.%20He%20was%20recently%20charged%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20for%20threatening%20Sikhs%20to%20avoid%20flying%20on%20Air%20India.%20He%20had%20also%20threatened%20to%20prevent%20Air%20India%20from%20operating%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%2C%20citing%20multiple%20sources%2C%20said%20that%20it%20was%20not%20clear%20whether%20the%20protest%20to%20New%20Delhi%20led%20the%20plotters%20to%20abandon%20their%20plan%2C%20or%20whether%20the%20FBI%20intervened%20and%20thwarted%20a%20scheme%20already%20in%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20said%20that%20the%20US%20warning%20was%20issued%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Washington%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20also%20%E2%80%9Cinformed%20some%20allies%20about%20the%20plot%20following%20the%C2%A0murder%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20Sikh%20separatist%20killed%20in%20Vancouver%20in%20June%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20have%20filed%20a%20sealed%20indictment%20against%20at%20least%20one%20alleged%20perpetrator%20of%20the%20plot%20in%20a%20New%20York%20district%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20US%20justice%20department%20is%20debating%20whether%20to%20unseal%20the%20indictment%20and%20make%20the%20allegations%20public%20or%20wait%20until%20Canada%20finishes%20its%20investigation%20into%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20murder.%20Further%20complicating%20the%20case%2C%20one%20person%20charged%20in%20the%20indictment%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20left%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20proceedings%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20FT%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20noted%20that%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department%20and%20FBI%20refused%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20National%20Security%20Council%20told%20FT%20that%20the%20US%20does%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20comment%20on%20ongoing%20law%20enforcement%20matters%20or%20private%20diplomatic%20discussions%20with%20our%20partners%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CUpholding%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20US%20citizens%20is%20paramount.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20US%20embassy%20in%20India%20repeated%20the%20NSC%E2%80%99s%20response.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20comment%20on%20diplomatic%2C%20law%20enforcement%2C%20or%20intelligence%20discussions%20with%20our%20partners%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20response%20issued%20late%20on%20Wednesday%20night%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20did%20not%20address%20the%20issue%20that%20the%20US%20had%20lodged%20a%20protest%2C%20but%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20Americans%20had%20shared%20%E2%80%9Cinputs%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20New%20Delhi%20was%20cooperating%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20course%20of%20recent%20discussions%20on%20India-US%20security%20cooperation%2C%20the%20US%20side%20shared%20some%20inputs%20pertaining%20to%20nexus%20between%20organized%20criminals%2C%20gun%20runners%2C%20terrorists%20and%20others.%20The%20inputs%20are%20a%20cause%20of%20concern%20for%20both%20countries%20and%20they%20decided%20to%20take%20necessary%20follow%20up%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20Bagchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20stated%20that%20India%20takes%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20inputs%20seriously%20since%20it%20impinges%20on%20our%20own%20national%20security%20interests%20as%20well%E2%80%9D.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fstrong%3EIssues%20in%20the%20context%20of%20US%20inputs%20are%20already%20being%20examined%20by%20relevant%20departments%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Bagchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20September%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20said%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20pointing%20towards%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar.%20India%20had%20dismissed%20those%20allegations%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmotivated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20countries%20expelled%20a%20senior%20diplomat%20each%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20measure.%20But%2C%20India%20went%20further%20asking%20for%20parity%20in%20diplomatic%20representation%2C%20which%20led%20Canada%20to%20withdraw%2041%20diplomats.%20Additionally%2C%20India%20paused%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%2C%20which%20were%20only%20restarted%20two%20months%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20response%20to%20the%20FT%20article%2C%20admitting%20that%20%E2%80%9Cinputs%E2%80%9D%20had%20been%20received%20from%20the%20US%20and%20were%20being%20%E2%80%9Cexamined%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20belligerent%20retaliation%20to%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20US%20had%20shared%20details%20of%20the%20Pannun%20case%20with%20%E2%80%9Csome%20allies%E2%80%9D%20after%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing%20in%20June%2C%20Washington%20widened%20the%20circle%20to%20more%20countries%20after%20Trudeau%20went%20public%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Csparked%20concern%20among%20allies%20about%20a%20possible%20pattern%20of%20behaviour%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20consistently%20asked%20India%20to%20join%20the%20Canadian%20investigation%2C%20with%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Anthony%20Blinken%20having%20raised%20it%20last%20week%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20US%20ambassador%20to%20Canada%20David%20Cohen%20had%20also%20said%20that%20information%20received%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Five%20Eyes%E2%80%99%20intelligence%20sharing%20network%20had%20contributed%20to%20Trudeau%20going%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeveral%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20debate%20inside%20the%20Biden%20administration%20said%20officials%20were%20aware%20that%20any%20public%20disclosure%20of%20the%20US%20plot%2C%20and%20Washington%E2%80%99s%20protest%20to%20New%20Delhi%2C%20would%20renew%20questions%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20reliability%20as%20a%20trusted%20partner%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20FT%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700657477000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22215159%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-22-at-9.45.19-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-unravelled-plot-to-kill-khalistani-separatist-lodged-protest-with-india-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20not%20referring%20to%20a%20US%20protest%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%20admitted%20that%20Washington%20%E2%80%9Cshared%20some%20inputs%20pertaining%20to%20nexus%20between%20organised%20criminals%2C%20gun%20runners%2C%20terrorists%20and%20others%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-unravelled-plot-to-kill-khalistani-separatist-lodged-protest-with-india-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ghosts%20Will%20Always%20Haunt%20Stolen%20Land%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22161733%2FPalestine_Flag_at_Parliament_House.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20reading%20an%20account%20of%20the%20October%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20the%20kibbutzim%20located%20near%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20been%20under%20sieged%20by%20Israel%20for%20decades%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20lament%20of%20those%20who%20lived%20there%20about%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20paradise%20that%20the%20community%20was%20to%20be%2C%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20a%20short%20story%20by%20Premchand%20titled%20%3Cem%3EBalidan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Sacrifice).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ways%20of%20literature%20are%20strange.%20A%20poem%20or%20a%20story%20written%20in%20an%20entirely%20different%20time%20and%20context%20surfaces%20when%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20your%20present.%20Lying%20somewhere%20in%20the%20deep%20recess%20of%20your%20subconscious%2C%20it%20surfaces%20suddenly%20as%20reality%20shocks%20you.%20At%20times%2C%20it%20clears%20the%20mist.%20And%20there%20are%20times%20it%20complicates%20what%20appears%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWritten%20in%20folkloric%20style%2C%20%3Cem%3EBalidan%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20Israel%20or%20Palestine.%20It%20does%20not%20even%20talk%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20violence%20that%20the%20inhabitants%20of%20the%20kibbutzim%20faced.%20It%20is%20a%20simple%20story%20which%20tells%20you%20about%20Girdhari%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20small%20farmer%20Harkhu.%20After%20Harkhu%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20moneylenders%20lay%20a%20trap%20for%20Girdhari%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20loan.%20While%20the%20pretext%20is%20to%20help%20him%2C%20when%20the%20debt%20rises%2C%20they%20force%20him%20to%20part%20with%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGirdhari%20is%20deeply%20attached%20to%20his%20land.%20Every%20inch%20of%20the%20land%20is%20soaked%20with%20his%20blood%2C%20Premchand%20writes.%20But%20he%20has%20no%20way%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20falling%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20greedy%20moneylenders.%20He%20is%20forced%20to%20become%20a%20labourer.%20Then%20he%20disappears.%20Those%20who%20have%20usurped%20his%20land%20want%20to%20use%20it.%20But%20when%20they%20go%20to%20the%20farmland%2C%20they%20see%20Girdhari%20standing%20at%20the%20fence.%20When%20they%20try%20to%20talk%20to%20him%2C%20he%20disappears.%20It%20strikes%20horror%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20those%20who%20have%20usurped%20the%20land%20by%20deceiving%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGirdhari%20guards%20his%20land.%20Or%2C%20is%20it%20his%20ghost%3F%20Either%20way%2C%20those%20who%20had%20stolen%20it%20cannot%20enjoy%20the%20land.%20The%20ghost%20of%20Girdhari%20haunts%20the%20land%20and%20them.%20The%20land%20remains%20deserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20came%20to%20my%20mind%20when%20I%20read%20an%20account%20of%20the%20horrendous%20attack%20on%20the%20Kibbutz%20Nir%20Oz.%20It%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-palestinians-kibbutz-gaza-hamas-war-c3a7e8d87c5d19ecb0f7a57fe4f7f657%5C%22%3Etitled%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CRuins%20and%20memories%20of%20a%20paradise%20lost%20in%20an%20Israeli%20village%20where%20attackers%20killed%2C%20kidnapped%20dozens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20paradise%20%E2%80%93%20as%20all%20kibbutzim%20were%20to%20be.%20But%20it%20turned%20into%20a%20killing%20field.%20The%20%E2%80%9Cbarbarians%E2%80%9D%20had%20bloodied%20this%20beautiful%20idea.%20But%20should%20it%20have%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20kibbutzim%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20community%20members%2C%20who%20returned%20after%20the%20carnage%2C%20reminiscing%20about%20his%20lost%20life%2C%20told%20the%20reporter%2C%20%E2%80%9CLong%20before%20the%20attack%E2%80%A6on%20days%20when%20the%20kibbutz%E2%80%99s%20air%20raid%20siren%20warned%20of%20rocket%20fire%20from%20Gaza%2C%20holding%20on%20to%20that%20dream%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20was%20a%20grave%20injustice%20to%20the%20dreamers%20of%20Nir%20Oz.%20But%20they%20were%20aware%20of%20the%20lurking%20ghosts.%20The%20air%20raid%20siren%2C%20the%20rocket%20fire%20from%20Gaza%20and%20the%20safe%20rooms%20in%20all%20the%20houses%20in%20the%20kibbutz%20tell%20you%20that%20the%20dream%20was%20uneasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENir%20Oz%20overlooks%20Gaza.%20Sachar%20Butler%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Nir%20Oz%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20lost%20many%20friends%E2%80%A6%20We%20worked%20the%20fields%20until%20the%20last%20yard%20and%20always%20hoped%20that%20maybe%20one%20day%20there%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20be%20something%20peaceful%20%E2%80%A6%20between%20us%20and%20the%20other%20side.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cother%20side%E2%80%9D%20is%20Gaza.%20From%20where%20those%20who%20wrecked%20this%20serenity%20came.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20Nir%20Oz%20breaks%20our%20hearts.%20Think%20about%20the%20trauma%20that%20Sachar%20and%20other%20survivors%20of%20the%20attack%20will%20go%20through.%20Occasional%20rocket%20fires%20they%20were%20aware%20of.%20But%20they%20never%20expected%20such%20devastation.%20It%20will%20change%20them%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22162028%2Fgaza-israel-barrier.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22162028%2Fgaza-israel-barrier.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22162028%2Fgaza-israel-barrier-300x184.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685931%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20barrier%20between%20Israel%20and%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20%C2%A0IDF%20Spokesperson%E2%80%99s%20Unit%2C%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gaza%2C%20a%20stone%E2%80%99s%20throw%20away%20from%20Nir%20Oz%2C%20Ahmed%20Abu-Tawahina%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Community%20Mental%20Health%20Programme%20(GCMHP)%20explained%20to%20Dr%20Rajaie%20Batniji%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20of%20trauma%20makes%20no%20sense%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20context%20where%20people%20live%20in%20constant%20fear.%20Trauma%20makes%20sense%20in%20Geneva%2C%20where%20there%20is%20safety%2C%20stability%2C%20and%20routine.%20But%20in%20Gaza%2C%20there%20is%20no%20normalcy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmed%20suggested%20that%20an%20alternative%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctrauma%E2%80%9D%20might%20be%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emousiba%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20meaning%20tragedy.%20Since%20Gazans%20live%20in%20constant%20fear%20and%20insecurity%2C%20they%20are%20not%20typically%20shocked%20by%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20different%20are%20the%20psychologies%20of%20the%20two%20neighbours%2C%20the%20kibbutzim%20and%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Rajaie%20Batniji%20was%20shocked%20to%20find%20that%20violence%20is%20so%20intrinsic%20to%20their%20daily%20lives%20that%20it%20does%20not%20shock%20the%20Gazans.%20Batniji%20experienced%20it%20himself%2C%20when%20he%20was%20bidding%20farewell%20to%20his%20family%20members%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20long%20farewell%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20my%20departure%2C%20my%20extended%20family%20assembled%20for%20a%20group%20photograph.%20Children%20climbed%20onto%20their%20siblings%20and%20mothers.%20Everyone%20shuffled%20into%20view%20of%20the%20lens.%20Then%2C%20the%20house%20shook%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20an%20explosion.%20I%20jumped%20in%20fear.%20Yet%20young%20and%20old%20relatives%20remained%20smiling%20for%20the%20camera.%20They%20were%20unfazed%2C%20despite%20the%20knowledge%20that%20an%20Israeli%20military%20jet%20had%20dropped%20a%20bomb%20somewhere%20just%20east%20of%20us.%20My%20uncle%2C%20Abu%20Nizar%2C%20explained%20their%20calm%3A%20%E2%80%98When%20you%20are%20living%20in%20hell%2C%20and%20someone%20turns%20up%20the%20heat%20a%20little%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20change%20much.%20You%E2%80%99re%20still%20in%20hell.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20posed%20for%20some%20more%20photographs%20with%20bounding%20smiles%2C%20and%20without%20asking%20about%20the%20death%20and%20destruction%20that%20surrounded%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20will%20definitely%20talk%20about%20the%20lasting%20trauma%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Nir%20Oz%20and%20other%20kibbutzim%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20must.%20But%20why%20is%20it%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20themselves%20say%20that%20they%20are%20beyond%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unjust%20for%20some%20violent%20men%20to%20destroy%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20utopia.%20But%20it%20is%20also%20unjust%20for%20an%20entire%20society%20to%20live%20continuously%20in%20%3Cem%3Emousiba.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReading%20about%20the%20occasional%20scare%20of%20rockets%20fired%20from%20Gaza%2C%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20another%20essay%20by%20Salman%20Abu%20Sitta.%20He%20quotes%20a%20member%20of%20another%20kibbutz%2C%20Adele.%20She%20is%20upset%20with%20the%20kites%20and%20balloons%20that%20fly%20from%20Gaza%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.timesofisrael.com%2Fwhile-the-south-burns-again%2F%5C%22%3Edestroy%20her%20fields%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CLast%20year%20I%20started%20a%20Google%20Map%20to%20show%20as%20many%20of%20the%20fires%20that%20were%20started%20by%20flaming%20kites%20and%20balloons%20launched%20from%20Gaza%2C%20as%20I%20could.%20These%20tools%20of%20arson%20are%20launched%20to%20destroy%20that%20which%20we%2C%20and%20those%20who%20came%20before%20us%2C%20have%20built%20and%20nurtured.%20To%20set%20our%20fields%20ablaze.%20To%20destroy%20the%20beautiful%20forests%20which%20many%20of%20you%20have%20paid%20for%20over%20the%20decades%2C%20through%20JNF.%20All%20those%20trees%20you%20planted%20in%20memory%20of%20loved%20ones%2C%20to%20commemorate%20happy%20occasions%2C%20or%20just%20to%20green%20Israel%20and%20%E2%80%98make%20the%20desert%20bloom%E2%80%99.%20They%20are%20the%20targets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20Abu%20Sitta%20is%20sadly%20amused%20at%20her%20indignation.%20He%20also%20finds%20Adele%E2%80%99s%20cousin%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20McGill%20University%2C%20pathetically%20ignorant%20when%20he%20praises%20the%20settlers%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfarmers%20who%20even%20under%20fire%20continue%20reaching%20out%20to%20their%20Gazan%20neighbors%2C%20confusing%20the%20world%20with%20their%20remarkable%20Jewish%2C%20Zionist%20and%20democratic%20generosity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%2C%20according%20to%20the%20professor%2C%20Hamas%20does%20not%20understand.%20He%20wonders%20why%20this%20kibbutz%20Nirim%20is%20routinely%20attacked%20even%20after%20most%20of%20its%20members%20are%20generous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20tells%20Adele%20that%20the%20land%20she%20is%20using%20as%20a%20farm%20was%20his%20land%3A%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20my%20wheat%20fields.%20I%20told%20her%20that%20I%20remember%20as%20a%20child%20being%20allowed%20to%20sit%20on%20our%20combine%20harvester.%E2%80%9D%20Adele%20wants%20proof%20and%20he%20refuses%20to%20satisfy%20her%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20refused%20to%20answer.%20I%20could%20have%20replied%20that%20Abu%20Sitta%20name%20was%20on%20Allenby%20maps%20when%20he%20took%20Beer%20Sheba%20in%201917%2C%20that%20my%20great-great-grandfather%20was%20mentioned%20by%20name%20in%20an%201845%20Ottoman%20document%20copied%20in%20Cairo%20and%20Jerusalem.%20I%20could%20have%20said%20that%20the%20name%20Abu%20Sitta%20(Father%20of%20Six)%20was%20coined%20in%20about%201720%20on%20account%20of%20my%20early%20ancestor%20was%20a%20well-known%20knight%20accompanied%20by%20six%20companions%2Fguards.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20refused%20to%20answer%20because%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20prove%20my%20heritage%20to%20a%20settler%20whose%20relatives%20came%20from%20the%20shtetl%20to%20the%20shores%20of%20Palestine%20in%20a%20smuggler%E2%80%99s%20ship%20in%20the%20dead%20of%20night.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20feels%20humiliated%20when%20asked%20to%20prove%20his%20heritage%20to%20a%20settler%20like%20Adele.%3