80%98new%20world%E2%80%99%20she%20was%20introduced%20to%20and%20went%20on%20to%20pursue%20a%20BTech%2C%20MTech%20and%20PhD%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20enjoyed%20learning%20biochemistry%2C%20preservation%2C%20processing%2C%20and%20research%20of%20food%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20education%2C%20the%20food%20technologist%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20choose%20a%20job%20of%20her%20liking%2C%20but%20here%E2%80%99s%20where%20her%20other%20dream%20kicks%20in%20%E2%80%94%20to%20be%20her%20own%20boss.%20And%20she%20was%20willing%20to%20put%20in%20the%20work%20and%20wait%20for%20her%20chance%20in%20the%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20chance%20presented%20itself%20even%20before%20the%20entrepreneur%20completed%20her%20PhD%2C%20and%20led%20to%20the%20launch%20of%20her%20food%20venture%20%E2%80%98Khalis%20Foods%E2%80%99.%20Today%2C%20Rukhsaar%20has%20managed%20to%20convert%20her%20passion%20into%20a%20thriving%20career%2C%20and%20is%20also%20among%20the%20top%20eight%20finalists%20of%20MasterChef%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20mission%20to%20provide%20unadulterated%20food%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20713px)%20100vw%2C%20713px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frukhsaar22-1700564266.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22713%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rukhsaar%20sells%20healthy%20treats%20for%20kids%20through%20her%20venture%20Khalis%20foods%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frukhsaar22-1700564266.jpeg%20713w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frukhsaar22-1700564266-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frukhsaar22-1700564266-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frukhsaar22-1700564266-