E2%80%99s%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20control%20their%20children%20given%20their%20own%20traumas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_359258809_3473669876218453_1571985264835777987_n_1080-1700226813.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ya_All%20team%20speaking%20to%20children%20at%20a%20relief%20camp%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_359258809_3473669876218453_1571985264835777987_n_1080-1700226813.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_359258809_3473669876218453_1571985264835777987_n_1080-1700226813-300x158.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_359258809_3473669876218453_1571985264835777987_n_1080-1700226813-500x264.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_359258809_3473669876218453_1571985264835777987_n_1080-1700226813-768x405.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_359258809_3473669876218453_1571985264835777987_n_1080-1700226813-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334389%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22570%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EYa_All%20team%20speaking%20to%20children%20at%20a%20relief%20camp.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20help%20of%20our%20transgender%20team%2C%20we%20started%20going%20to%20these%20relief%20camps%20with%20access%20to%20a%20field%20and%20offered%20football%20training%20to%20these%20children.%20These%20training%20sessions%20would%20last%20a%20week%20in%20one%20relief%20camp%20before%20we%20would%20visit%20another%20and%20s