334390%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221896%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENancy%20is%20a%20powerhouse%20of%20talent.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20path%20to%20fame%20has%20been%20a%20rather%20difficult%20one%20for%20Nancy.%20She%20started%20by%20making%20transition%20videos%2C%20where%20she%20would%20showcase%20a%20dress%20stitched%20by%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20buying%20the%20camera%20and%20the%20equipment%2C%20we%20had%20to%20decide%20what%20videos%20to%20shoot.%20I%20used%20to%20watch%20a%20lot%20of%20transition%20videos%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20try%20my%20hand%20at%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nancy%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConceptualised%2C%20stitched%20and%20presented%20by%20her%20while%20her%20brother%20shoots%20it%2C%20these%20videos%20had%20hardly%20any%20takers.%20Most%20of%20the%20videos%20had%20about%20400%20views%2C%20she%20adds.%20Undeterred%2C%20she%20continued%20posting%20everyday%2C%20for%201.5%20years.%20Even%20then%2C%20the%20number%20of%20views%20hardly%20increased.%20Some%20videos%20got%20over%20a%20thousand%20views.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrainstorming%20with%20her%20younger%20brother%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echange%20strategies%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20these%20videos%20were%20not%20working.%20The%20shopping%20website%20Meesho%E2%80%99s%20hauls%20were%20trending%20then%2C%20and%20she%20decided%20to%20try%20that.%20The%20twist%2C%20she%20tried%2C%20was%20some%20over-the-top%20dancing%20and%20acting%20in%20the%20videos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20very%20dedicated%20to%20this%20project.%20I%20put%20in%20as%20much%20effort%20and%20too